#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:122
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Here's a screenshot of &konqueror;"
msgid "Here’s a screenshot of &konqueror;"
msgstr "अत्र &konqueror;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <interface>Titlebar</interface> is the strip across the top of "
#| "&konqueror;'s window, and operates in the same way as for other &kde; "
#| "applications. <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the central "
#| "portion to bring up the neat Titlebar menu."
msgid ""
"The <interface>Titlebar</interface> is the strip across the top of "
"&konqueror;’s window, and operates in the same way as for other &kde; "
"applications. <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the central portion "
"to bring up the neat Titlebar menu."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Titlebar</interface> &konqueror; इत्यस्य विण्डो इत्यस्य उपरिभागे स्थिता "
"पट्टिका अस्ति, अन्येषां &kde; अनुप्रयोगाः। <mousebutton>राइट्</mousebutton> "
"केन्द्रीयभागे क्लिक् कृत्वा सुव्यवस्थितं Titlebar मेन्यू उपरि आनयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Menubar</interface> is the strip containing the names of the "
"drop-down menus. <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a name to "
"alternately show and hide that menu, or use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>the underlined letter</keycap></keycombo> in the name as a hot key, "
"for example <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> to "
"show the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu. The various menus are described in "
"the <link linkend=\"menubar\">Menubar</link> section of this document."
msgstr ""
"द<interface> मेनूबार</interface> ड्रॉप्-डाउन मेन्यू-नामानि समाविष्टा पट्टिका अस्ति ।"
"<mousebutton> वामः</mousebutton> तत् मेनू क्रमेण दर्शयितुं गोपयितुं च नाम क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु, "
"अथवा उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &amp;अल्ट्;<keycap> रेखांकितम् अक्षरम्</"
"keycap></keycombo> नाम्नि उष्णकीलरूपेण यथा<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &amp;अल्ट्;"
"<keycap> ई</keycap></keycombo> दर्शयितुं<guimenu> सम्पादन</guimenu> मेनू। विभिन्नाः "
"मेनूः वर्णिताः सन्ति<link linkend=\"menubar\"> मेनूबार</link> अस्य दस्तावेजस्य विभागः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Toolbar</interface> contains icons for commonly used "
"operations. <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> clicking on an icon will "
"activate it. A brief description of what that icon does will appear when you "
"hover the pointer over it."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Toolbar</interface> इत्यत्र सामान्यतया प्रयुक्तानां कार्याणां चिह्नानि सन्ति "
"। <mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> चिह्नं नुत्वा तत् सक्रियं भविष्यति । यदा भवन्तः तस्य "
"उपरि सूचकं स्थापयन्ति तदा तत् चिह्नं किं करोति इति संक्षिप्तं वर्णनं दृश्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some icons, for example the Up and Back icons in the previous screenshot, "
"have a small black arrow at the right. If you click with the &LMB; at this "
"arrow a small dropdown menu will appear."
msgstr ""
"केचन चिह्नानि, उदाहरणार्थं पूर्वस्क्रीन्शॉट् मध्ये Up तथा Back चिह्नानि, दक्षिणभागे "
"लघुकृष्णबाणं भवन्ति । यदि भवान् &LMB; अस्मिन् बाणे लघु ड्रॉप्डाउन मेन्यू दृश्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on the <interface>Toolbar</"
#| "interface> will bring up the <link linkend=\"rmb-menus"
#| "\"><guilabel>Toolbar Settings</guilabel> menu</link> which you can use to "
#| "change the <interface>Toolbar</interface>'s appearance and position."
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on the <interface>Toolbar</"
"interface> will bring up the <link linkend=\"rmb-menus\"><guilabel>Toolbar "
"Settings</guilabel> menu</link> which you can use to change the "
"<interface>Toolbar</interface>’s appearance and position."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>दक्षिणः</mousebutton> इत्यत्र क्लिक् कृत्वा<interface> टूलबार</"
"interface> उपस्थापयिष्यति<link linkend=\"rmb-menus\"><guilabel> टूलबार सेटिंग्स्</"
"guilabel> मेनू</link> यस्य उपयोगेन भवन्तः परिवर्तनं कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति<interface> टूलबार</"
"interface> &#39;s रूपं पदं च ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Location Toolbar</interface> shows the path to the directory, "
"&URL; or file being viewed. You can type a path or &URL; here and press "
"<keysym>Enter</keysym> or <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on the "
"<guiicon>Go</guiicon> icon at the right hand end of the <interface>Location "
"Toolbar</interface> to go to it. The black icon at the right hand end of the "
"<interface>Location Toolbar</interface> clears the text entry box."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Location Toolbar</interface> निर्देशिकायाः मार्गं दर्शयति, &URL; अथवा "
"सञ्चिका दृश्यते। भवान् मार्गं अथवा &URL; अत्र <keysym>Enter</keysym> नुदन्तु अथवा "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> नुदन्तु गन्तुं <interface>Location Toolbar</"
"interface> इत्यस्य दक्षिणहस्तस्य अन्ते <guiicon>Go</guiicon> चिह्नं नुदन्तु तस्मै । "
"<interface>Location Toolbar</interface> इत्यस्य दक्षिणहस्तस्य अन्ते स्थितं कृष्णवर्णीयं "
"चिह्नं पाठप्रविष्टिपेटीं स्वच्छं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Bookmark Toolbar</interface> is the area under the "
"<interface>Location Toolbar</interface> in the previous screenshot. You can "
"add frequently used bookmarks here; see the <link linkend=\"bookmarks"
"\">Organizing Your Bookmarks</link> section of this document."
msgstr ""
"द<interface> बुकमार्क टूलबार</interface> इत्यस्य अधः क्षेत्रम् अस्ति<interface> स्थान "
"साधनपट्टी</interface> पूर्वस्मिन् स्क्रीनशॉट् मध्ये । अत्र बहुधा प्रयुक्तानि पुस्तकचिह्नानि "
"योजयितुं शक्नुवन्ति; पश्यन्तु इति<link linkend=\"bookmarks\"> भवतः बुकमार्कस्य आयोजनम्</"
"link> अस्य दस्तावेजस्य विभागः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <interface>Window</interface> is the main area of &konqueror; and can "
#| "show you the contents of a directory, web page, document or image. Using "
#| "the <link linkend=\"menu-window\"><guimenu>Window</guimenu></link> menu "
#| "you can split &konqueror;'s main window into one or more separate views, "
#| "useful for drag and drop operations, or set it to contain two or more "
#| "tabbed views."
msgid ""
"The <interface>Window</interface> is the main area of &konqueror; and can "
"show you the contents of a directory, web page, document or image. Using the "
"<link linkend=\"menu-window\"><guimenu>Window</guimenu></link> menu you can "
"split &konqueror;’s main window into one or more separate views, useful for "
"drag and drop operations, or set it to contain two or more tabbed views."
msgstr ""
"द<interface> कोष्ठ</interface> इति मुख्यक्षेत्रं &amp;konqueror; तथा च निर्देशिकायाः, "
"जालपुटस्य, दस्तावेजस्य वा चित्रस्य वा सामग्रीं दर्शयितुं शक्नोति । प्रयुज्य<link linkend="
"\"menu-window\"><guimenu> कोष्ठ</guimenu></link> menu भवान् &amp;konqueror; "
"इत्यस्य मुख्यविण्डो एकस्मिन् वा अधिकेषु पृथक् दृश्येषु विभक्तुं शक्नोति, यत् drag and drop "
"क्रियाणां कृते उपयोगी भवति, अथवा द्वौ वा अधिकौ ट्याब्ड् दृश्यौ समाविष्टौ इति सेट् कर्तुं "
"शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <interface>Status Bar</interface> runs across the bottom of the "
#| "&konqueror;'s window and often shows general information about whatever "
#| "the mouse pointer is hovering over. If you have split the main window "
#| "into a number of views you will get a Status Bar for each view, and it "
#| "will include a small green light at the left hand end to show which is "
#| "the <quote>active</quote> view. <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking "
#| "on the Status Bar brings up the Status Bar <link linkend=\"rmb-menus"
#| "\"><mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> Mouse Button Menu</link>."
msgid ""
"The <interface>Status Bar</interface> runs across the bottom of the "
"&konqueror;’s window and often shows general information about whatever the "
"mouse pointer is hovering over. If you have split the main window into a "
"number of views you will get a Status Bar for each view, and it will include "
"a small green light at the left hand end to show which is the <quote>active</"
"quote> view. <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on the Status Bar "
"brings up the Status Bar <link linkend=\"rmb-menus\"><mousebutton>Right</"
"mousebutton> Mouse Button Menu</link>."
msgstr ""
"द<interface> स्थिति पट्टी</interface> &amp;konqueror;&#39;s विण्डो इत्यस्य अधः "
"धावति तथा च प्रायः मूषकसूचकः यत्किमपि उपरि भ्रमति तस्य विषये सामान्यसूचनाः दर्शयति । "
"यदि भवान् मुख्यविण्डो कतिपयेषु दृश्येषु विभक्तवान् तर्हि प्रत्येकस्य दृश्यस्य कृते Status Bar "
"प्राप्स्यति, तथा च तस्मिन् वामहस्तस्य अन्ते लघु हरितप्रकाशः समाविष्टः भविष्यति यत् दर्शयति "
"यत् कोऽपि<quote> सक्रियं</quote> दृश्यं।<mousebutton> दक्षिणः</mousebutton> Status "
"Bar इत्यत्र क्लिक् करणेन Status Bar इत्येतत् दृश्यते<link linkend=\"rmb-menus"
"\"><mousebutton> दक्षिणः</mousebutton> माउस बटन मेनू</link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Don't worry if your &konqueror; doesn't look exactly like this "
#| "screenshot; it is highly configurable. In particular:"
msgid ""
"Don’t worry if your &konqueror; doesn’t look exactly like this screenshot; "
"it is highly configurable. In particular:"
msgstr ""
"चिन्ता मा कुरुत यदि भवतः &konqueror; अस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् इव सम्यक् न दृश्यते; अत्यन्तं "
"विन्यासयोग्यं भवति । विशेषतः :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the <link linkend=\"menu-settings\"><guimenu>Settings</guimenu></"
"link> menu to choose whether to show or hide the Menubar, Main Toolbar, "
"Location Toolbar and Bookmark Toolbar, or even to add an Extra Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"भवन्तः उपयोक्तुं शक्नुवन्ति<link linkend=\"menu-settings\"><guimenu> सेटिंग्स्</"
"guimenu></link> menu इत्यनेन Menubar, Main Toolbar, Location Toolbar तथा "
"Bookmark Toolbar दर्शयितुं वा गोपनं वा इति चयनं कर्तुं, अथवा Extra Toolbar योजयितुं "
"अपि ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the toolbars are unlocked, you can also drag them to a new position by "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking on the handle at the left hand end "
"of a bar and move it around by holding the &LMB; down while you drag it."
msgstr ""
"यदि साधनपट्टिकाः अनलॉक् कृताः सन्ति तर्हि भवन्तः तान् <mousebutton>left</"
"mousebutton> इत्यनेन पट्टिकायाः वामहस्तस्य अन्ते स्थितं हन्डलं क्लिक् कृत्वा अपि नूतनस्थानं "
"प्रति कर्षितुं शक्नुवन्ति तथा च &LMB; अधः यदा भवन्तः तत् कर्षन्ति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For more details of how to change &konqueror;'s appearance, see the <link "
#| "linkend=\"config\">Configuring &konqueror;</link> section"
msgid ""
"For more details of how to change &konqueror;’s appearance, see the <link "
"linkend=\"config\">Configuring &konqueror;</link> section."
msgstr ""
"&amp;konqueror; इत्यस्य स्वरूपं कथं परिवर्तयितव्यम् इति अधिकविवरणार्थं पश्यन्तु<link "
"linkend=\"config\"> विन्यस्तं कुर्वन् &amp;konqueror;</link> खंड"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:195
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Tooltips and What's This?"
msgid "Tooltips and What’s This?"
msgstr "साधनसूचनानि तथा च एतत् किम्?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can find out a lot about how &konqueror; works without needing to "
#| "read this entire document if you take advantage of <guilabel>Tooltips</"
#| "guilabel> and the <guimenuitem>What's This?</guimenuitem> feature."
msgid ""
"You can find out a lot about how &konqueror; works without needing to read "
"this entire document if you take advantage of <guilabel>Tooltips</guilabel> "
"and the <guimenuitem>What’s This?</guimenuitem> feature."
msgstr ""
"कथं &konqueror; यदि भवान् <guilabel>Tooltips</guilabel> तथा "
"<guimenuitem>What's This?</guimenuitem> इति विशेषतायाः लाभं लभते तर्हि एतत् सम्पूर्णं "
"दस्तावेजं पठितुं आवश्यकतां विना कार्यं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you hover the mouse pointer over a Toolbar tab button it should bring "
"up a terse description of what that button does."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवान् मूषकसूचकं Toolbar ट्याब् बटन् उपरि स्थापयति तदा तत् बटन् किं करोति इति संक्षिप्तं "
"वर्णनं आनेतव्यम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenuitem>What's This?</guimenuitem> is invoked by the Menubar "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>What's This?</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> item or by <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;"
#| "<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo>. It changes the cursor to show a question "
#| "mark alongside the arrow."
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>What’s This?</guimenuitem> is invoked by the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>What’s This?</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> item or by <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F1</"
"keycap></keycombo>. It changes the cursor to show a question mark alongside "
"the arrow."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>इदं किम्?</guimenuitem> इति मेनुबार <menuchoice><guimenu>सहाय</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>इदं किम्?</guimenuitem></menuchoice> इति मदेन अथवा "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\" इत्यनेन आह्वयते । >&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap></"
"keycombo> इति । बाणस्य पार्श्वे प्रश्नचिह्नं दर्शयितुं कर्सर परिवर्तयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When this question mark is visible, a &LMB; click won't actually do "
#| "anything until you have clicked on a control (or the text alongside it) "
#| "that supports <guimenuitem>What's This?</guimenuitem>, in which case it "
#| "will display a reasonably comprehensive description of what the control "
#| "does. Most of the dialog boxes that &konqueror; brings up support the "
#| "<guimenuitem>What's This?</guimenuitem> feature."
msgid ""
"When this question mark is visible, a &LMB; click won’t actually do anything "
"until you have clicked on a control (or the text alongside it) that supports "
"<guimenuitem>What’s This?</guimenuitem>, in which case it will display a "
"reasonably comprehensive description of what the control does. Most of the "
"dialog boxes that &konqueror; brings up support the <guimenuitem>What’s This?"
"</guimenuitem> feature."
msgstr ""
"यदा एतत् प्रश्नचिह्नं दृश्यते तदा &LMB; क्लिक् वस्तुतः किमपि न करिष्यति यावत् भवान् "
"<guimenuitem>What's This?</guimenuitem> समर्थयति इति नियन्त्रणे (अथवा तस्य पार्श्वे "
"पाठं) क्लिक् न करोति, अस्मिन् सति नियन्त्रणं किं करोति इति यथोचितरूपेण व्यापकं वर्णनं "
"प्रदर्शयिष्यति अधिकांशः संवादपेटिकाः ये &konqueror; <guimenuitem>What's This?</"
"guimenuitem> इति विशेषतायाः समर्थनं आनयति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> and <mousebutton>Middle</mousebutton> Mouse "
"Button Actions"
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> तथा <mousebutton>मध्य</mousebutton> "
"मूषकबटनक्रियाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you click the &LMB; on an item in &konqueror;'s window, it will be "
#| "<quote>activated</quote>. Thus"
msgid ""
"If you click the &LMB; on an item in &konqueror;’s window, it will be "
"<quote>activated</quote>. Thus"
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् &LMB; &konqueror; इत्यस्य विण्डो मध्ये कस्मिंश्चित् द्रव्ये, तत् <quote>सक्रियम्</"
"quote> भविष्यति । इत्थम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on an icon in the Toolbar to perform "
"the action that icon represents."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> चिह्नं यत् कार्यं प्रतिनिधियति तत् कार्यं कर्तुं Toolbar "
"मध्ये कस्यापि चिह्नस्य उपरि क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on an item in the Menubar to make that "
"menu drop down."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> Menubar मध्ये कस्यापि द्रव्यस्य उपरि क्लिक् कृत्वा तत् "
"मेनू ड्रॉप् डाउन करणीयम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a menu item to do that thing."
msgstr "<mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> तत् कार्यं कर्तुं मेन्यू-वस्तुं नुदन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on an icon in the Bookmark Toolbar to "
"open that &URL;."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> तत् &URL; उद्घाटयितुं Bookmark Toolbar इत्यस्मिन् "
"चिह्ने क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a link in a web page to make "
"&konqueror; follow that link."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> जालपुटे कस्मिंश्चित् लिङ्के क्लिक् कृत्वा &konqueror; तस्य "
"लिङ्कस्य अनुसरणं कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a folder icon or name and "
"&konqueror; will descend into (show the contents of) that folder."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> एकं समुच्चय चिह्नं वा नाम वा क्लिक् कृत्वा &konqueror; "
"तस्मिन् पुटे अवतरति (तस्य सामग्रीं दर्शयति) ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a file name or icon and "
#| "&konqueror; will do whatever it thinks appropriate, based on the file "
#| "type. In general this means opening <acronym>HTML</acronym> pages, or "
#| "previewing text, image or &okular; documents, showing them within "
#| "&konqueror;'s window (<quote>Preview</quote> means that you can see the "
#| "file but not change it)."
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a file name or icon and &konqueror; "
"will do whatever it thinks appropriate, based on the file type. In general "
"this means opening <acronym>HTML</acronym> pages, or previewing text, image "
"or &okular; documents, showing them within &konqueror;’s window "
"(<quote>Preview</quote> means that you can see the file but not change it)."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> सञ्चिकानाम वा चिह्नं वा क्लिक् कृत्वा &konqueror; "
"यत्किमपि उचितं मन्यते तत् करिष्यति, सञ्चिकाप्रकारस्य आधारेण । सामान्यतया अस्य अर्थः "
"<acronym>HTML</acronym> पृष्ठानि उद्घाटयितुं, अथवा पाठस्य, चित्रस्य अथवा &okular; "
"documents, &konqueror;'s window इत्यस्य अन्तः दर्शयित्वा (<quote>Preview</quote> "
"इत्यस्य अर्थः अस्ति यत् भवान् सञ्चिकां द्रष्टुं शक्नोति परन्तु परिवर्तयितुं न शक्नोति) ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&konqueror; decides what the file type is by matching the filename "
#| "extension against a list of known types. If that fails it tries to guess "
#| "the type from the file contents. You can change the list of known file "
#| "types and associated actions with the <guilabel>File Associations</"
