"it in a new &konqueror; window, unless the <guilabel>Open links in new tab "
"instead of in new window</guilabel> box has been checked in the "
"<guimenuitem>General</guimenuitem> page of the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog. &konqueror; can open links on pages and "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu></menuchoice>, as well as the "
"<guibutton>Home</guibutton>, <guibutton>Up</guibutton>, <guibutton>Back</"
"guibutton> and <guibutton>Forward</guibutton> entries in a new tab or window."
msgstr ""
"&MMB इत्यत्र क्लिक् कृत्वा; सञ्चिकायां वा पुटस्य नाम वा चिह्नस्य उपरि मूलतः "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> क्लिक् करणं समानं करोति व्यतिरिक्तं यत् सामान्यतया "
"नूतने &konqueror; विण्डो, यावत् <menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu>< इत्यस्य "
"<guimenuitem>सामान्य</guimenuitem> पृष्ठे <guilabel>नवीनविण्डोमध्ये न अपितु नूतनट्याब् "
"मध्ये लिङ्कानि उद्घाटयन्तु</guilabel> इति पेटी परीक्षिता नास्ति "
"guimenuitem>Konqueror...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> संवादं विन्यस्यताम् । "
"&konqueror; पृष्ठेषु तथा <menuchoice><guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu></menuchoice> "
"इत्यत्र लिङ्कानि उद्घाटयितुं शक्नोति, तथैव <guibutton>गृहं</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>उपरि</guibutton>, <guibutton>पृष्ठतः</ . guibutton> तथा "
"<guibutton>अग्रे</guibutton> प्रविष्टयः नूतने ट्याब् अथवा विण्डो मध्ये ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Holding the &Shift; key down while pressing the &MMB; will open the link in "
"the background."
msgstr "धारयन् &Shift; &MMB; पृष्ठभूमितः लिङ्कं उद्घाटयिष्यति।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> Mouse Button Menus"
msgstr "<mousebutton>दक्षिण</mousebutton> मूषकबटनमेनू"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Clicking the &RMB; on almost any part of &konqueror;'s window will bring "
#| "up an appropriate context menu."
msgid ""
"Clicking the &RMB; on almost any part of &konqueror;’s window will bring up "
"an appropriate context menu."
msgstr ""
"&RMB इत्यत्र क्लिक् कृत्वा; &konqueror;'s window इत्यस्य प्रायः कस्मिन् अपि भागे समुचितं "
"सन्दर्भमेनू आनयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you have enabled the <guilabel>Right click goes back in history</"
#| "guilabel> option in &konqueror;'s <link linkend=\"othersettings\"> "
#| "configuration</link> settings a simple <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
