"then just press <keysym>Enter</keysym>."
msgstr ""
"उपपुटे अवतरितुं <mousebutton>वामतः </mousebutton> तस्य नाम वा चिह्नं वा क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु "
"-- अथवा यदि भवान् पूर्वमेव <quote>चयनितवान्</quote> (अधः पश्यन्तु) -- तर्हि केवलं "
"<keysym>Enter</ नुदन्तु । कील्यम्>।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To go up the folder tree you can click on the <guiicon>Up</guiicon> button "
"in the Toolbar, use<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Up</keysym></"
"keycombo>, or use the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Up</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option."
msgstr ""
"पुटवृक्षस्य उपरि गन्तुं भवान् Toolbar मध्ये <guiicon>Up</guiicon> बटन् नुदतु,<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Up</keysym></keycombo> इत्यस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं, अथवा "
"उपयोक्तुं शक्नोति मेनूबार <menuchoice><guimenu>गो</guimenu><guimenuitem>उपरि</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <quote>select</quote> a file or folder in the displayed folder without "
"opening it in any way use the <keysym>up</keysym> and <keysym>down </keysym> "
"arrow keys to move through the items. The selected item will be highlighted "
"and some information about it will be displayed in the Status Bar."
msgstr ""
"प्रदर्शितपुटे सञ्चिकां वा पुटं वा <quote>चयनं</quote> कर्तुं तत् किमपि प्रकारेण न उद्घाट्य "
"<keysym>up</keysym> तथा <keysym>down </keysym> बाणकुंजीयोः उपयोगं कृत्वा वस्तूनि "
"गन्तुम् चयनितं द्रव्यं प्रकाशितं भविष्यति तस्य विषये काश्चन सूचनाः Status Bar मध्ये "
"प्रदर्शिताः भविष्यन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Setting the <link linkend=\"viewmode\">View Mode</link> to <guimenuitem> "
"Details</guimenuitem> can help you locate folders in the tree below the "
"current folder; in this mode each folder is shown with a small box at the "
"left. If the box contains a <keycap>&gt;</keycap> sign, <mousebutton>left </"
