"यदा भवान् नूतनपुटं गतः तदा भवान् Toolbar <guiicon>Back</guiicon> बटन्, Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem इत्यस्य "
"उपयोगेन स्वस्य पूर्वपरिचयं प्रति गन्तुं शक्नोति ></menuchoice> मदं, अथवा <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>वाम</keysym></keycombo> । एकदा भवन्तः पुनः "
"गतवन्तः तदा भवन्तः अग्रे गन्तुं शक्नुवन्ति। टूल्बार <guiicon>अग्रे</guiicon> बटनस्य, मेनूबार "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>गच्छ</guimenu> <guimenuitem>अग्रे</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> मदस्य अथवा <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keysym>सत्यम्</"
"keysym></keycombo> इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can also choose to enter the parent folder by clicking on "
"the Toolbar <guiicon>Up</guiicon>, the <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Up</guimenuitem></menuchoice> item, or with <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Up</keysym></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"वैकल्पिकरूपेण, भवान् Toolbar <guiicon>Up</guiicon>, <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Up</guimenuitem></menuchoice> इति मदं नुत्वा मातापितृपुटं "
"प्रविष्टुं अपि चयनं कर्तुं शक्नोति , अथवा <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Up</"
"keysym></keycombo> इत्यनेन सह ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the checkmark at the right of the toolbar <guiicon>Up</guiicon>, "
"<guiicon>Back</guiicon> or <guiicon>Forward</guiicon> buttons or selecting "
"these items in the <guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu brings up a submenu of "
"recently visited locations."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon>Up</guiicon>, <guiicon>Back</guiicon> अथवा <guiicon>Forward</"
"guiicon> बटन् इत्यस्य दक्षिणभागे स्थितं चेकमार्कं नुदन्तु अथवा <guimenu>Go</guimenu> "
"इत्यस्मिन् एतानि वस्तूनि चयनं कुर्वन्तु menu इत्यनेन सद्यः एव गतानां स्थानानां उपमेनू आगच्छति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding Files and Folders"
msgstr "सञ्चिकाः पुटं च अन्वेष्टुम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:660
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you don't know or can't remember where a file or folder is within your "
#| "system, then use the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</"
#| "keycap></keycombo> or the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Find File...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option. This "
#| "starts the file finder application &kfind;. See the <ulink url=\"help:/"
#| "kfind/index.html\">&kfind; Handbook</ulink> for help in using &kfind;."
msgid ""
"If you don’t know or can’t remember where a file or folder is within your "
"system, then use the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</"
"keycap></keycombo> or the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Find File…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option. This "
"starts the file finder application &kfind;. See the <ulink url=\"help:/kfind/"
"index.html\">&kfind; Handbook</ulink> for help in using &kfind;."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् न जानाति अथवा स्मर्तुं न शक्नोति यत् भवतां प्रणाल्याः अन्तः सञ्चिका अथवा पुटं "
"कुत्र अस्ति, तर्हि <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> इति शॉर्टकट् अथवा Menubar इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>उपकरणं</guimenu><guimenuitem>सञ्चिकां अन्वेष्टुम्...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पः । एतेन &kfind; इति सञ्चिका-अन्वेषक-अनुप्रयोगः "
"आरभ्यते । <ulink url=\"help:/kfind/index.html\">&kfind; &kfind;-उपयोगे सहायतार्थं "
"हस्तपुस्तिका</ulink> इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the name of a file or folder begins with a period (dot), then it is a "
"<quote>hidden</quote> file or folder, and will not normally be shown by "
"&konqueror;. To see hidden files or folders use the Menubar <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Hidden Files</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"option."
msgstr ""
"यदि सञ्चिकायाः अथवा पुटस्य नाम अवधिना (बिन्दु) आरभ्यते, तर्हि सा <quote>गुप्त</quote> "
"सञ्चिका अथवा पुटम् अस्ति, सामान्यतया &konqueror; द्वारा न दर्शितं भविष्यति । "
"गुप्तसञ्चिकाः अथवा पुटं द्रष्टुं Menubar <menuchoice> <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Hidden Files</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> विकल्पस्य उपयोगं "
"कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another reason &konqueror; may not show the file or folder you are looking "
"for is that you may have the <link linkend=\"konq-plugin\"><guilabel> "
"Directory Filter</guilabel></link> plugin set to display only certain types "
"of file."
msgstr ""
"अन्यत् कारणम् &amp;konqueror; भवन्तः अन्विष्यमाणां सञ्चिकां वा पुटं वा न दर्शयितुं शक्नुवन्ति "
"यत् भवन्तः...<link linkend=\"konq-plugin\"><guilabel> निर्देशिका फ़िल्टर</"
"guilabel></link> प्लगिन् केवलं कतिपयप्रकारस्य सञ्चिकां प्रदर्शयितुं सेट् कृतः ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removable Devices"
msgstr "हटनीयानि उपकरणानि"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:680
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Any removable device (USB stick, floppy disk, &CD; drive or other hard "
#| "disk partition that you have on your system) will usually appear in the "
#| "<filename class=\"directory\">/ </filename>, <filename class=\"directory"
#| "\">/media</filename>, <filename class=\"directory\">/mnt</filename> or "
#| "<filename class=\"directory\">/auto</filename> folder, having a path "
#| "something like <filename class=\"directory\">/mnt/floppy</filename> or "
#| "<filename class=\"directory\">/cdrom</filename>. The details will depend "
#| "on how your system was set up."
msgid ""
"Any removable device (USB stick, &CD; drive or other hard disk partition "
"that you have on your system) will usually appear in the <filename class="
"\"directory\">/</filename>, <filename class=\"directory\">/media</filename>, "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/mnt</filename> or <filename class=\"directory"
"\">/auto</filename> folder, having a path something like <filename class="
"\"directory\">/mnt/floppy</filename> or <filename class=\"directory\">/"
"cdrom</filename>. The details will depend on how your system was set up."
msgstr ""
"यत्किमपि हटनीयं यन्त्रं (USB स्टिक, फ्लॉपी डिस्क, &CD; ड्राइव् अथवा अन्यं हार्डडिस्क "
"विभाजनं यत् भवतां प्रणाल्यां अस्ति) प्रायः <filename class=\"directory\">/ </"
"filename>, <filename class=\"directory\">/माध्यम</filename>, <filename class="
"\"directory\">/mnt</filename> अथवा <filename class=\"directory\">/स्वयम्</"
"filename> पुटे, <filename class=\"directory\">/mnt/floppy</filename> अथवा "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/cdrom</filename> इत्यादि किमपि मार्गं कृत्वा । "
"विवरणं भवतः प्रणाली कथं स्थापिता इति अवलम्बते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&UNIX; / &Linux; requires that you <command>mount</command> a removable "
"device when you have inserted it into the drive, and <command>mount </"
"command> other hard disk partitions when you want to access them. You also "
"need to unmount a removable device before removing it to register that it is "
"no longer available."
msgstr ""
"&UNIX; / & लिनक्स; अपेक्षते यत् भवन्तः <command>mount</command> एकं हटनीयं यन्त्रं यदा "
"भवन्तः तत् ड्राइव् मध्ये सम्मिलितवन्तः, तथा च <command>mount </command> अन्य हार्डडिस्क "
"विभाजनानि यदा भवन्तः तान् अभिगन्तुं इच्छन्ति भवद्भिः अपि हटनीयं यन्त्रं निष्कासयितुं पूर्वं "
"अनमाउण्ट् करणीयम् यत् तत् पुनः उपलब्धं नास्ति इति पञ्जीकरणं कर्तुं ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid "How you do this will depend on your system setup:"
msgstr "भवन्तः एतत् कथं कुर्वन्ति इति भवतः सिस्टम् सेटअप इत्यस्य उपरि निर्भरं भविष्यति:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the <guilabel>Device Notifier</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>यन्त्रसूचक</guilabel> इत्यस्य उपयोगः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In a &kde; session the <ulink url=\"help:/plasma-desktop/index.html#device-"
"notifier\">Device Notifier</ulink> window will popup, when you insert a "
"removable device and allows you to select an appropriate application for "
"this media or only mount the device."
msgstr ""
"एकस्मिन् &kde; session <ulink url=\"help:/plasma-desktop/index.html#device-"
"notifier\">यन्त्रसूचकः</ulink> विण्डो पॉपअप भविष्यति, यदा भवान् हटनीयं यन्त्रं सम्मिलितं "
"करोति तथा च अस्य माध्यमस्य कृते समुचितं अनुप्रयोगं चयनं कर्तुं शक्नोति अथवा केवलं यन्त्रं माउण्ट् "
"कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you use the <guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> layout for your desktop "
#| "you may have icons for removable devices on your desktop, in which case "
#| "&LMB; click on the icon to mount it. Doing this should also bring up a "
#| "&konqueror; window showing the contents of the device. To unmount, "
#| "<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on the icon and choose the "
#| "<guimenuitem>Unmount</guimenuitem> item. Visit the section <link linkend="
#| "\"making\">Create New...</link> in this Handbook to see how to create "
#| "such an icon."
msgid ""
"If you use the <guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> layout for your desktop, you "
"may have icons for removable devices on your desktop, in which case &LMB; "
"click on the icon to mount it. Doing this should also bring up a &konqueror; "
"window showing the contents of the device. To unmount, <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click on the icon and choose the <guimenuitem>Unmount</"
"guimenuitem> item. Visit the section <link linkend=\"making\">Create New…</"
"link> in this Handbook to see how to create such an icon."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवन्तः उपयुञ्जते<guilabel> समुच्चय दृश्यम्</guilabel> भवतः डेस्कटॉप् कृते layout भवतः "
"डेस्कटॉप् मध्ये हटनीयानां उपकरणानां चिह्नानि भवितुम् अर्हन्ति, अस्मिन् सन्दर्भे &amp;LMB; तत् "
"माउण्ट् कर्तुं चिह्नं नुदन्तु । एवं कृत्वा &amp;konqueror; यन्त्रस्य सामग्रीं दर्शयति विण्डो । "
"अनमाउण्ट् कर्तुं, २.<mousebutton> दक्षिणः</mousebutton> चिह्नं क्लिक् कृत्वा "
"चिनोतु<guimenuitem> अनमाउंट</guimenuitem> वस्तु। विभागं पश्यन्तु<link linkend="
"\"making\"> नूतनं रचयतु...</link> एतादृशं चिह्नं कथं निर्मातव्यम् इति द्रष्टुं अस्मिन् "
"Handbook मध्ये ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Or you can do it the traditional way by typing into a text console window:"
msgstr "अथवा पाठकन्सोल् विण्डो मध्ये टङ्कयित्वा पारम्परिकरीत्या कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति:"

#. Tag: command
#: index.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid "mount /mnt/floppy"
msgstr "mount /mnt/फ्लॉपी"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "to mount, for example, the floppy drive, and"
msgstr "माउण्ट् कर्तुं, उदाहरणार्थं, फ्लॉपी ड्राइव्, तथा च"

#. Tag: command
#: index.docbook:704
#, no-c-format
msgid "umount /mnt/floppy"
msgstr "umount /mnt/फ्लॉपी"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"to unmount it (<command>umount</command> not <command>unmount</command>)."
msgstr ""
"तत् अनमाउण्ट् कर्तुं (<command>umount</command> न तु <command>unmount</command>) ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:707
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Rather than having to open a text console to type the <command>mount </"
#| "command> or <command>umount</command> commands, you may prefer to use "
#| "&konqueror;'s <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Execute "
#| "Shell Command</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
#| "\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) feature."
msgid ""
"Rather than having to open a text console to type the <command>mount </"
"command> or <command>umount</command> commands, you may prefer to use "
"&konqueror;’s <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Execute Shell "
"Command</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) feature."
msgstr ""
"<command>mount </command> अथवा <command>umount</command> आदेशान् टङ्कयितुं "
"पाठकन्सोल् उद्घाटयितुं न अपि तु &konqueror;इत्यस्य <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu> इत्यस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं रोचते <guimenuitem>शेल् आदेशं निष्पादयन्तु</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) "
"विशेषता।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting Files and Folders"
msgstr "सञ्चिकाः पुटं च विलोपनम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; gives you two ways to dispose of an unwanted file or folder:"
msgstr "&konqueror; अवांछितसञ्चिकायाः अथवा पुटस्य निष्कासनस्य द्वौ उपायौ ददाति:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:727
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can move it to the <filename>Trash</filename> folder, which is the "
"safest method as you can get it back if you realize that you have made a "
"mistake."
msgstr ""
"भवान् तत् <filename>Trash</filename> पुटं प्रति स्थानान्तरयितुं शक्नोति, यत् सुरक्षिततमं "
"विधिः यतः भवान् तत् पुनः प्राप्तुं शक्नोति यदि भवान् अवगच्छति यत् भवान् त्रुटिं कृतवान् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:731
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can just plain Delete it, which removes the entry from the folder and "
#| "adds the disk area occupied by the file(s) to the system's list of free "
#| "disk areas, in the same way as the <command>rm</command> command."
msgid ""
"You can just plain Delete it, which removes the entry from the folder and "
"adds the disk area occupied by the file(s) to the system’s list of free disk "
"areas, in the same way as the <command>rm</command> command."
msgstr ""
"भवान् केवलं साधारणं Delete it कर्तुं शक्नोति, यत् पुटतः प्रविष्टिं निष्कासयति तथा च "
"सञ्चिका(भिः) व्याप्तं डिस्कक्षेत्रं प्रणाल्याः मुक्तडिस्कक्षेत्रसूचौ योजयति, यथा <command>rm</"
"command> आदेशः ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:735
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you want to use this feature check the option <guilabel>Show 'Delete' "
#| "menu entries which bypass the trashcan</guilabel> on the <guilabel>File "
#| "Management</guilabel> settings page."
msgid ""
"If you want to use this feature check the option <guilabel>Show “Delete” "
"menu entries which bypass the trashcan</guilabel> on the <guilabel>File "
"Management</guilabel> settings page."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् एतत् विशेषतां उपयोक्तुं इच्छति तर्हि <guilabel>'Delete' मेनूप्रविष्टयः दर्शयतु ये "
"<guilabel>सञ्चिकाप्रबन्धन</guilabel> सेटिंग्स् पृष्ठे trashcan</guilabel> इत्येतत् बाईपासं "
"कुर्वन्ति इति विकल्पं परीक्ष्यताम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The simplest way to remove a file or folder is to position the mouse pointer "
"over its name or icon and press the &RMB;, which will bring up a menu "
"containing the options <guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"सञ्चिकां वा पुटं वा निष्कासयितुं सरलतमः उपायः अस्ति यत् मूषकसूचकं तस्य नाम अथवा चिह्नस्य "
"उपरि स्थापयित्वा &RMB; </guimenuitem> इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Or, if you have <quote>selected</quote> the item, the Menubar <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> menu will give you the choice of <quote><guimenuitem>Move to Trash</"
"guimenuitem></quote> and <quote><guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem></quote> "
"options."
msgstr ""
"अथवा, यदि भवान् <quote>चयनितवान्</quote> द्रव्यं, तर्हि Menubar <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> मेन्यू भवन्तं <quote><guimenuitem>कचरेषु गच्छतु</guimenuitem></quote> इति "
"विकल्पं दास्यति तथा <quote><guimenuitem>विलोपन</guimenuitem></quote> विकल्पाः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>Del</keycap> will move the selected item or items to Trash."
msgstr "<keycap>Del</keycap> चयनितं द्रव्यं वा द्रव्यं वा Trash मध्ये स्थानान्तरयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo> will "
"really, truly and irrevocably delete the selected item or items."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo> चयनितं द्रव्यं "
"वा द्रव्यं वा वास्तवतः, यथार्थतया, अनिवार्यतया च विलोपयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:756
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You won't be able to remove a file or folder if you don't have the "
#| "necessary permissions."
msgid ""
"You won’t be able to remove a file or folder if you don’t have the necessary "
"permissions."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवतां समीपे आवश्यकाः अनुमतिः नास्ति तर्हि भवान् सञ्चिकां वा पुटं वा हर्तुं न शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving and Copying"
msgstr "चालनं प्रतिलिपिकरणं च"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid "To copy a file or subfolder between folders you can:"
msgstr "पुटयोः मध्ये सञ्चिकायाः उपपुटस्य वा प्रतिलिपिं कर्तुं भवान् कर्तुं शक्नोति:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Position the mouse pointer over its name or icon and hold down the &RMB;, "
"which will bring up a menu containing the <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> "
"option. Choose that."
msgstr "मूषकसूचकं तस्य नाम अथवा चिह्नस्य उपरि स्थापयित्वा &RMB; तत् चिनुत।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Or if the item is <quote>selected</quote> you can use the <guiicon>Copy</"
"guiicon> button on the Toolbar or the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem></menuchoice> item, or the <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> shortcut key "
"combination. You can also select <link linkend=\"selection\">multiple</link> "
"files or folders to copy/move as well."
msgstr ""
"अथवा यदि द्रव्यम् अस्ति<quote> चयनितम्</quote> भवन्तः उपयोक्तुं शक्नुवन्ति<guiicon> "
"प्रतिलिपि</guiicon> बटनं Toolbar अथवा Menubar इत्यत्र<menuchoice><guimenu> "
"सम्पादन</guimenu><guimenuitem> प्रतिलिपि</guimenuitem></menuchoice> द्रव्यम्, "
"अथवा<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &amp;Ctrl;<keycap> ग</keycap></keycombo> "
"शॉर्टकट कील संयोजन। भवन्तः अपि चयनं कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति<link linkend=\"selection\"> बहु</"
"link> सञ्चिकाः अथवा पुटं प्रतिलिपिं कर्तुं/चलितुं अपि।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigate to the folder you want to copy the item into then Paste the item "
"into the new folder by using the Toolbar <guiicon>Paste</guiicon> button or "
"the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option or the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> shortcut, or by moving the mouse pointer to a "
"clear area of the window and holding the &RMB; down to bring up a menu "
"containing the <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> option."
msgstr ""
"यस्मिन् पुटे गच्छतु यस्मिन् द्रव्यं प्रतिलिखितुं इच्छति ततः Toolbar <guiicon>Paste</"
"guiicon> बटन् अथवा Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Paste इत्यस्य उपयोगेन नूतनपुटे द्रव्यं चिनोतु </guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"विकल्पः अथवा <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> "
"इति विकल्पः shortcut, अथवा मूषकसूचकं विण्डो इत्यस्य स्पष्टक्षेत्रे स्थानान्तरयित्वा &RMB; "
"<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> विकल्पं युक्तं मेनू आनेतुं अधः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moving a file or subfolder between folders can be done in the same way as "
"copying, except that you choose the <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> option or "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> instead of "
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>. The item that you have <guimenuitem>Cut</"
"guimenuitem> will be removed from the original folder when you do the "
"<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> into the new folder."
msgstr ""
"पुटयोः मध्ये सञ्चिकायाः उपपुटस्य वा स्थानान्तरणं प्रतिलिपिकरणस्य समानरूपेण कर्तुं शक्यते, केवलं "
"यत् भवान् <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> विकल्पं अथवा <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap> इति विकल्पं चिनोति <guimenuitem>प्रतिलिपि</"
"guimenuitem> इत्यस्य स्थाने </keycombo> इति । भवता यत् द्रव्यं <guimenuitem>Cut</"
"guimenuitem> अस्ति तत् मूलपुटात् निष्कासितम् भविष्यति यदा भवान् नूतनपुटे "
"<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> करोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:801
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Using Drag 'n Drop"
msgid "Using Drag’n Drop"
msgstr "Drag 'n Drop इत्यस्य उपयोगः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; also supports Drag and Drop copying and moving of files and "
"folders."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; अपि च Drag and Drop प्रतिलिपिं कृत्वा सञ्चिकानां, पुटस्य च स्थानान्तरणं च "
"समर्थयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:806
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can do this by having two instances of &konqueror;, one showing the "
#| "folder you want to copy from, the other showing the target folder. "
#| "Position the mouse pointer over the item you wish to copy or move, then, "
#| "holding the &LMB; pressed, <quote>drag</quote> it to a clear space in the "
#| "target folder. Release the button and you will be presented with a menu "
#| "choice of <guimenuitem>Copy Here</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Move Here</"
#| "guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Link Here</guimenuitem>. Take care to "
#| "<quote>drop</quote> the item into an empty area of the target folder view "
#| "- dropping it on top of a subfolder will copy or move the item into that "
#| "folder."
msgid ""
"You can do this by having two instances of &konqueror;, one showing the "
"folder you want to copy from, the other showing the target folder. Position "
"the mouse pointer over the item you wish to copy or move, then, holding the "
"&LMB; pressed, <quote>drag</quote> it to a clear space in the target folder. "
"Release the button and you will be presented with a menu choice of "
"<guimenuitem>Copy Here</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Move Here</guimenuitem> "
"or <guimenuitem>Link Here</guimenuitem>. Take care to <quote>drop</quote> "
"the item into an empty area of the target folder view—dropping it on top of "
"a subfolder will copy or move the item into that folder."
msgstr ""
"भवान् &konqueror;इत्यस्य द्वौ उदाहरणौ कृत्वा एतत् कर्तुं शक्नोति, एकः यत् पुटं प्रतिलिखितुं "
"इच्छति तत् दर्शयति, अन्यत् लक्ष्यपुटं दर्शयति । मूषकसूचकं यस्य द्रव्यस्य उपरि प्रतिलिखितुं वा "
"स्थानान्तरितुं वा इच्छति तस्य उपरि स्थापयतु, ततः, &LMB; नुदन्, <quote>कर्षयन्तु</quote> "
"लक्ष्यपुटे स्पष्टस्थाने । बटनं मुक्तं कुर्वन्तु ततः भवन्तः <guimenuitem>अत्र प्रतिलिपिं कुर्वन्तु</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>अत्र गच्छन्तु</guimenuitem> अथवा <guimenuitem>अत्र "
"लिङ्क् कुर्वन्तु</guimenuitem> इति मेनूपरिचयः प्रस्तुतः भविष्यति । लक्ष्यपुटदृश्यस्य रिक्तक्षेत्रे "
"द्रव्यं <quote>निपात</quote> कर्तुं सावधानं कुर्वन्तु - उपपुटस्य उपरि पातयित्वा द्रव्यं तस्मिन् "
"पुटे प्रतिलिपिं करिष्यति वा स्थानान्तरयिष्यति वा"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also set up &konqueror; to show more than one folder within its "
"window and drag &amp; drop between them."
msgstr ""
"भवन्तः &konqueror; तस्य विण्डोमध्ये एकादशाधिकं पुटं दर्शयितुं तथा &amp; तयोः मध्ये पातयति।"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:823
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split Views for Drag &amp; Drop"
msgstr "Drag &amp; बिन्दुः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:827
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This screenshot illustrates the use of the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Split View Left/Right</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option, also available with the shortcut <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo>, to split the "
"main &konqueror; window into two views, each showing the contents of a "
"different folder."
msgstr ""
"अयं स्क्रीनशॉट् Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Split "
"View Left/Right</guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पस्य उपयोगं दर्शयति, यत् "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"> इति शॉर्टकट् इत्यनेन सह अपि उपलभ्यते &Ctrl;&Shift;"
"<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo>, मुख्यं विभक्तुं &konqueror; विण्डो इत्यस्य द्वयोः "
"दृश्ययोः मध्ये प्रत्येकं भिन्नस्य पुटस्य सामग्रीं दर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To be able to show different folders in each view they should not be linked; "
"the little boxes at the bottom right of each view should be empty."
msgstr ""
"प्रत्येकस्मिन् दृश्ये भिन्नानि पुटं दर्शयितुं शक्नुवन् तेषां लिङ्क् न कर्तव्यम्; प्रत्येकस्य दृश्यस्य अधः "
"दक्षिणभागे स्थिताः लघुपेटिकाः शून्याः भवेयुः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>active</quote> view, that is the one whose path is shown in the "
"Location Toolbar and which responds to navigation and Menubar commands, is "
"shown by the little green light in the bottom left corner. To make a view "
"active, <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on an empty area of the view "
"or on its Status Bar."
msgstr ""
"<quote>सक्रिय</quote> दृश्यं, यत् यस्य मार्गः Location Toolbar मध्ये दर्शितः अस्ति तथा "
"च यः navigation तथा Menubar आदेशानां प्रतिक्रियां ददाति, तत् अधः वामकोणे किञ्चित् "
"हरितप्रकाशेन दर्शितम् अस्ति दृश्यं सक्रियं कर्तुं <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> दृश्यस्य "
"रिक्तक्षेत्रे अथवा तस्य Status Bar इत्यत्र क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:844
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To remove an active view from &konqueror;'s window use the <keycombo "
#| "action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> shortcut, or "
#| "the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Window</guimenu><guimenuitem>Close "
#| "Active View</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option, or &RMB; click on the "
#| "Status Bar and choose the <guimenuitem>Close View</guimenuitem> option "
#| "from the resulting menu."
msgid ""
"To remove an active view from &konqueror;’s window use the <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> shortcut, or the "
"Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Window</guimenu><guimenuitem>Close Active View</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option, or &RMB; click on the Status Bar and "
"choose the <guimenuitem>Close View</guimenuitem> option from the resulting "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; इत्यस्य विण्डोतः सक्रियदृश्यं निष्कासयितुं <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> शॉर्टकट्, अथवा मेनूबार "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Window< इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु /"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>सक्रियदृश्यं बन्दं कुरुत</guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पः, "
"अथवा &RMB; Status Bar इत्यत्र क्लिक् कृत्वा परिणामितमेनूतः <guimenuitem>Close View</"
"guimenuitem> विकल्पं चिनोतु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use &konqueror; tabs, you can drag and drop between tabs by dragging "
"the file to the tab label, without letting go yet. The destination tab will "
"pop to the front, allowing you to continue dragging and then to drop the "
"file."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् &konqueror; tabs, भवन्तः सञ्चिकां tab label मध्ये कर्षयित्वा tabs मध्ये drag "
"and drop कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति, अद्यापि न त्यक्त्वा । गन्तव्यट्याब् अग्रे पोप् भविष्यति, येन भवन्तः "
"कर्षणं निरन्तरं कर्तुं ततः सञ्चिकां पातयितुं च शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duplicate File or Folder Names"
msgstr "सञ्चिकायाः अथवा पुटस्य नामानां द्वितीयकम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you try to paste a file or folder into a folder that already contains an "
"item with the same name, &konqueror; will pop up a dialog box warning you "
"that the item already exists. You can then choose to:"
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् सञ्चिकां वा पुटं वा तस्मिन् पुटे चिनोतुम् प्रयतते यस्मिन् पूर्वमेव समाननाम्ना द्रव्यं "
"भवति, &konqueror; एकं संवादपेटिकां पोप् अप करिष्यति यत् भवन्तं चेतयति यत् द्रव्यं पूर्वमेव "
"अस्ति । ततः भवान् इदं चयनं कर्तुं शक्नोति:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:862
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cancel the paste operation by pressing the <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr "<guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> इति बटन् नुत्वा पेस्ट् क्रियां रद्दं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Give the item that is being copied a different name. You can do this by "
"typing a new name into the text entry box or get &konqueror; to "
"<guibutton>Suggest New Name</guibutton>. When you have done this press the "
"<guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"यस्य द्रव्यस्य प्रतिलिपिः क्रियते तस्य भिन्नं नाम ददातु। पाठप्रविष्टिपेटिकायां नूतनं नाम "
"टङ्कयित्वा अथवा &konqueror; to <guibutton>नवनाम सुचयतु</guibutton> । यदा भवता "
"एतत् कृतं तदा <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> इति बटन् नुदन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have copied multiple items, <guibutton>Skip</guibutton> the current "
"item."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् बहुविधं द्रव्यं प्रतिलिखितवान् तर्हि वर्तमानं द्रव्यं <guibutton>Skip</"
"guibutton> ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Apply to All</guibutton> button can be used if you have "
"copied multiple items."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् बहुविधवस्तूनि प्रतिलिखितवान् तर्हि <guibutton>सर्वं प्रति प्रयोक्तुं</guibutton> "
"बटनस्य उपयोगः कर्तुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items in the View"
msgstr "View मध्ये Items इत्यस्य चयनम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several ways to select items in the view. Once a group of items is "
"selected, all actions, such as <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, and drag "
"and drop operations, affect all selected items."
msgstr ""
"दृश्ये द्रव्याणां चयनस्य अनेकाः उपायाः सन्ति । एकदा द्रव्यसमूहः चयनितः जातः चेत्, सर्वाणि "
"क्रियाणि, यथा <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>प्रतिलिपि</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem >Trash</guimenuitem></menuchoice> इत्यत्र गच्छन्तु, तथा "
"च drag and drop क्रियाः, सर्वाणि चयनितवस्तूनि प्रभावितयन्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:890
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Mouse"
msgstr "मूषकस्य उपयोगेन वस्तूनि चयनं करणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can press the &LMB; somewhere in the view and draw a rectangle around a "
"group of items before releasing the button. This will select all items in "
"the rectangle and clear the previous selection. If the &Shift; key is "
"pressed during the selection process, the previous selection is kept."
msgstr ""
"भवान् &LMB; दृश्ये कुत्रचित् तथा बटनं मुक्तं कर्तुं पूर्वं द्रव्यसमूहस्य परितः आयतं आकर्षयन्तु । एतेन "
"आयतस्य सर्वाणि वस्तूनि चित्वा पूर्वचयनं स्वच्छं भविष्यति । यदि &Shift; चयनप्रक्रियायाः समये "
"कीलं नुदति, पूर्वचयनं स्थापितं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Ctrl; key is pressed while an item is clicked with the &LMB;, the "
"selection state of this item is toggled. If the &Ctrl; key is pressed while "
"a rectangle is drawn around a group of items as described above, the "
"selection state of all items in the rectangle will be toggled."
msgstr ""
"यदि &Ctrl; कीलं नुद्यते यदा &LMB;सहितं द्रव्यं क्लिक् भवति, अस्य द्रव्यस्य चयनस्थितिः टॉग्ल् "
"भवति । यदि &Ctrl; कीलं नुदति यदा उपरि वर्णितं यथा आयतं द्रव्यसमूहं परितः आकृष्यते तदा "
"आयतस्य सर्वेषां द्रव्याणां चयनस्थितिः टॉग्ल् भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Shift; key is pressed while an item is clicked with the &LMB;, all "
"items between the previous current item and the clicked item will be "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"यदि &Shift; कीलं नुद्यते यदा &LMB;सहितं द्रव्यं क्लिक् क्रियते, पूर्ववर्तमानवस्तूनाम् क्लिक् "
"कृतस्य द्रव्यस्य च मध्ये सर्वाणि वस्तूनि चयनितानि भविष्यन्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:918
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Keyboard"
msgstr "कीबोर्डस्य उपयोगेन वस्तूनि चयनं करणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If an arrow key, <keysym>PgUp</keysym>, <keysym>PgDn</keysym>, <keycap>Home</"
"keycap>, or <keycap>End</keycap> is pressed, the new current item is "
"selected, and the previous selection is cleared."
msgstr ""
"यदि बाणकुंजी, <keysym>PgUp</keysym>, <keysym>PgDn</keysym>, <keycap>Home</"
"keycap>, अथवा <keycap>End</keycap> नुद्यते तर्हि नूतनं वर्तमानं द्रव्यं चयनं भवति , "
"पूर्वचयनं च स्वच्छं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:928
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Ctrl; key is held while one of the above keys is pressed, the "
"selection remains unchanged."
msgstr ""
"यदि &Ctrl; उपर्युक्तेषु कीलेषु एकं निपीड्यमानं कीलं धारितं भवति, चयनं अपरिवर्तितं तिष्ठति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Shift; key is held while one of the above keys is pressed, all items "
"between the previous current item and the new current item will be selected."
msgstr ""
"यदि &Shift; उपर्युक्तेषु कीलेषु एकं निपीड्यमानं कीलं धारितं भवति, पूर्ववर्तमानवस्तूनाम् "
"नूतनवर्तमानवस्तूनाञ्च मध्ये सर्वाणि वस्तूनि चयनितानि भविष्यन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:938
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>Space</keysym></keycombo> is "
"pressed, the selection state of the current item is toggled."
msgstr ""
"यदि <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>Space</keysym></keycombo> नुद्यते "
"तर्हि वर्तमानवस्तुनः चयनस्थितिः टॉग्ल् भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:943
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> selects all "
"items in the view."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> दृश्ये सर्वाणि "
"वस्तूनि चिनोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> "
"toggles the selection state of all items in the view."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> दृश्ये "
"सर्वेषां वस्तूनाम् चयनस्थितिं टॉग्ल् करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a file or folder by typing the first few letters of its name and the "
"first matching item is selected. To clear the selection and cancel the "
"keyboard search press &Esc; or wait longer than the timeout of 1 second."
msgstr ""
"तस्य नामस्य प्रथमानि कतिचन अक्षराणि टङ्कयित्वा सञ्चिकां वा पुटं वा चिनोतु ततः प्रथमं "
"मेलयुक्तं द्रव्यं चयनं भवति । चयनं स्वच्छं कर्तुं कीबोर्ड-अन्वेषणं रद्दं कर्तुं च &Esc; अथवा 1 "
"सेकण्डस्य समयसमाप्तेः अपेक्षया अधिकं प्रतीक्षां कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Menu"
msgstr "मेनू इत्यस्य उपयोगेन वस्तूनि चयनं करणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:968
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You sometimes want to delete, copy or move a number of files that are "
"similar in some way. For example you may wish to move all of the <filename "
"class=\"extension\">.png</filename> graphics files from one folder to "
"another. &konqueror; makes this easy by letting you select multiple files "
"based on similarities in their file names."
msgstr ""
"भवन्तः कदाचित् केनचित् प्रकारेण समानानि सञ्चिकानि विलोपयितुम्, प्रतिलिपिं कर्तुं वा "
"स्थानान्तरितुं वा इच्छन्ति । यथा भवन्तः सर्वाणि <filename class=\"extension\">.png</"
"filename> चित्रसञ्चिकाः एकस्मात् पुटे अन्यस्मिन् पुटे स्थानान्तरयितुम् इच्छन्ति । &konqueror; "
"तेषां सञ्चिकानामेषु समानतायाः आधारेण बहुविधसञ्चिकानां चयनं कर्तुं दत्त्वा एतत् सुलभं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:973
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
