"guimenu><guisubmenu>Selection</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Unselect Matching "
"Items…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option to specify which of the selected "
"files should be removed from the selection."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवान् सञ्चिकानां श्रेणीं चिनोति तदा भवान् Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Selection</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Uselect Matching "
"Items...</guimenuitem इत्यस्य उपयोगेन चयनं संकुचितं कर्तुं शक्नोति ></menuchoice> "
"विकल्पः चयनात् चयनितसञ्चिकासु काः निष्कासिताः इति निर्दिष्टुं ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Selection</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Unselect All</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option or "
"just &LMB; click on a clear area of the view to cancel the selection."
msgstr ""
"मेनूबार <menuchoice><guimenu>सम्पादनं</guimenu><guisubmenu>चयन</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>सर्वं अचयनं कुर्वन्तु</guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु "
"अथवा केवलं &LMB; चयनं रद्दीकर्तुं दृश्यस्य स्पष्टक्षेत्रे क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can even invert the selection: that is, deselect all selected files and "
"select those that were previously unselected. Use the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Selection</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Invert Selection</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option "
"or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> to "
"do this."
msgstr ""
"भवान् चयनं अपि विपर्ययितुं शक्नोति: अर्थात् सर्वाणि चयनितसञ्चिकाः अचयनं कृत्वा पूर्वं "
"अचयनितानि सञ्चिकाः चिनोतु । मेनूबार <menuchoice><guimenu>सम्पादयतु</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>चयनं</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>चयनं विपर्यय</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> विकल्पस्य अथवा <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;< इत्यस्य "
"उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> इति एतत् कर्तुं ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1013
