msgstr "सञ्चिकायाः अथवा निर्देशिकायाः मूलभूतलिङ्कः..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1061
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a symbolic link for local files or folder."
msgstr "स्थानीयसञ्चिकानां अथवा पुटस्य कृते प्रतीकात्मकं लिङ्कं रचयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1065
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Link to Application..."
msgid "Link to Application…"
msgstr "आवेदनस्य लिङ्क्..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1066
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is most useful if you want to create an icon that will open a "
"particular application. It opens a dialog box with several tabbed pages. The "
"first, <guilabel>General</guilabel>, is where you choose an icon and the "
"text that will appear with it. The second page, <guilabel>Permissions</"
"guilabel>, lets you select who can use or modify the icon. In the "
"<guilabel>Application</guilabel> page you must enter the <guilabel>Command</"
"guilabel> that will run the application, for example, <userinput>kwrite</"
"userinput> to start up the &kwrite; text editor. <userinput>kwrite /home/pam/"
"todo.txt</userinput> would open the file <filename>/home/pam/todo.txt</"
"filename> in &kwrite;. Advanced options such as the file types which the "
"application can open are also available from this page."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् एकं चिह्नं निर्मातुम् इच्छति यत् एकं विशेषं अनुप्रयोगं उद्घाटयिष्यति तर्हि एषः "
"विकल्पः सर्वाधिकं उपयोगी भवति । एतत् अनेकैः ट्याब्ड् पृष्ठैः सह संवादपेटिकां उद्घाटयति । "
"प्रथमं, <guilabel>सामान्य</guilabel>, यत्र भवान् चिह्नं चिनोति, तया सह दृश्यमानं पाठं च "
"चिनोति । द्वितीयं पृष्ठं <guilabel>अनुमतिः</guilabel> इति भवन्तं चिन्वितुं शक्नोति यत् "
"कोऽपि चिह्नस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं वा परिवर्तयितुं वा शक्नोति । <guilabel>अनुप्रयोग</guilabel> "
"पृष्ठे भवद्भिः <guilabel>आदेशः</guilabel> प्रविष्टव्यः यः अनुप्रयोगं चालयिष्यति, "
"उदाहरणार्थं, <userinput>kwrite</userinput> &kwrite; पाठ सम्पादक। "
"<userinput>kwrite /home/pam/todo.txt</userinput> इत्यनेन &kwrite; इत्यस्मिन् "
"<filename>/home/pam/todo.txt</filename> इति सञ्चिकां उद्घाटयिष्यति । "
"सञ्चिकाप्रकाराः इत्यादयः उन्नतविकल्पाः अपि अस्मात् पृष्ठात् उपलभ्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1078
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To make the application icon appear on your desktop, create the link in "
#| "your <filename class=\"directory\">~/Desktop</filename> folder (this may "
#| "be called something slightly different depending on how &kde; was "
#| "installed on your system) or get to the <guisubmenu>Create New...</"
#| "guisubmenu> sub menu by <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on a "
#| "free area of the desktop instead of within &konqueror;'s window."
msgid ""
"To make the application icon appear on your desktop, create the link in your "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/Desktop</filename> folder (this may be "
"called something slightly different depending on how &kde; was installed on "
"your system) or get to the <guisubmenu>Create New…</guisubmenu> sub menu by "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on a free area of the desktop "
"instead of within &konqueror;’s window."
msgstr ""
"अनुप्रयोगचिह्नं भवतः डेस्कटॉप् मध्ये दृश्यमानं कर्तुं, भवतः <filename class=\"directory\">~/"
"Desktop</filename> पुटे लिङ्कं रचयन्तु (भवतः प्रणाल्यां &kde; कथं संस्थापितम् इति अवलम्ब्य "
"एतत् किञ्चित् भिन्नं कथयितुं शक्यते) अथवा <guisubmenu>नवीन रचयतु...</guisubmenu> उपमेनू "
"प्रति <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> इत्यस्य स्थाने डेस्कटॉपस्य मुक्तक्षेत्रे क्लिक् कृत्वा "
"&konqueror;'s window इत्यस्य अन्तः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1085
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you have a lot of specialized application links and don't want to "
#| "clutter up the desktop, then why not create them in your Applications "
#| "folder. You can get there in &konqueror; by choosing "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Applications</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then create a single icon on your desktop to "
#| "open your Applications folder, which is usually in <filename class="
#| "\"directory\">~/.local/share/applications</filename>."
msgid ""
"If you have a lot of specialized application links and don’t want to clutter "
"up the desktop, then why not create them in your Applications folder. You "
"can get there in &konqueror; by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Applications</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then create a single "
"icon on your desktop to open your Applications folder, which is usually in "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share/applications</filename>."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवतां समीपे बहु विशेषानुप्रयोगलिङ्कानि सन्ति तथा च डेस्कटॉप् अव्यवस्थितं कर्तुम् न इच्छन्ति "
"तर्हि भवतः Applications समुच्चय मध्ये तान् किमर्थं न रचयन्तु । तत्र भवन्तः &konqueror; "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>गच्छ</guimenu> <guimenuitem>अनुप्रयोगाः</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> इति चित्वा । ततः स्वस्य Applications पुटं उद्घाटयितुं स्वस्य डेस्कटॉप् मध्ये एकं "
"चिह्नं रचयन्तु, यत् प्रायः <filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share/"
"applications</filename> इत्यत्र भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To put an application link icon into the panel, first create it in the "
"Applications folder then drag the icon onto a clear area of the panel."
msgstr ""
"फलकमध्ये एप्लिकेशनलिङ्क् चिह्नं स्थापयितुं प्रथमं Applications समुच्चय मध्ये रचयन्तु ततः चिह्नं "
"फलकस्य स्पष्टक्षेत्रे कर्षयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing Names and Permissions"
msgstr "नामानि अनुमतिः च परिवर्तयन्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The two easiest ways to change the name of a file or folder is to either "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on it and select <guimenuitem>Rename</"
"guimenuitem>, or select the file or folder and then press the <keycap>F2</"
"keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"सञ्चिकायाः अथवा पुटस्य नाम परिवर्तयितुं सुलभतमौ उपायौ अस्ति यत् <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> तस्मिन् क्लिक् कृत्वा <guimenuitem>Rename</guimenuitem> इति चिन्वन्तु, "
"अथवा सञ्चिकां वा पुटं वा चित्वा ततः <keycap नुदन्तु >F2</keycap> कीलम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the name or permissions of a file or folder <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click on its name or icon and select the "
"<guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> item, or if you have <quote>selected</"
"quote> the file or folder, then you can use the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Return</keycap></"
"keycombo>) option."
msgstr ""
"सञ्चिकायाः अथवा पुटस्य नाम वा अनुमतिं वा परिवर्तयितुं <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> तस्याः नाम वा चिह्नं वा क्लिक् कृत्वा <guimenuitem>Properties</"
"guimenuitem> मदं चिनोतु, अथवा यदि भवान् <quote>चयनितवान्</quote> अस्ति सञ्चिकां वा "
"पुटं वा, ततः भवान् Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> इत्यस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोति </"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>पुनरागमन</keycap></"
"keycombo>) विकल्पः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will bring up the Properties dialog box with several tabbed pages:"
msgstr "एतेन Properties संवादपेटिका अनेकैः ट्याब्ड् पृष्ठैः सह आगमिष्यति:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>General</guilabel>, which gives you some information about the "
"item and lets you change its name and, for a folder, the associated icon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>सामान्य</guilabel>, यत् भवन्तं द्रव्यस्य विषये काश्चन सूचनां ददाति तथा च तस्य "
"नाम परिवर्तयितुं शक्नोति तथा च, पुटस्य कृते, तत्सम्बद्धं चिह्नं परिवर्तयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1120
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Permissions</guilabel>, which shows you the item's ownership "
#| "and access permissions and lets you change the permissions."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Permissions</guilabel>, which shows you the item’s ownership and "
"access permissions and lets you change the permissions."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>अनुमतिः</guilabel>, यत् भवन्तं द्रव्यस्य स्वामित्वं अभिगमानुमतिः च दर्शयति तथा "
"च अनुमतिं परिवर्तयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy and Rename"
msgstr "प्रतिलिपिकृत्य पुनर्नामकरणं कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1127
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you want to make a copy of an existing file with a different name -- "
#| "perhaps as a backup -- in the same folder as the original file, do a "
#| "normal <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> then when you <guimenuitem>Paste</"
#| "guimenuitem> it a dialog box will pop up complaining that the file "
#| "already exists. Just type the new name into the dialog's text box and "
#| "press the <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button (or if you are feeling "
#| "lazy pressing the <guibutton>Suggest New Name</guibutton> button will "
#| "generate a new name for you)."
msgid ""
"If you want to make a copy of an existing file with a different name —"
"perhaps as a backup— in the same folder as the original file, do a normal "
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> then when you <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem> it a dialog box will pop up, complaining that the file already "
"exists. Just type the new name into the dialog’s text box and press the "
"<guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button (or if you are feeling lazy pressing "
"the <guibutton>Suggest New Name</guibutton> button will generate a new name "
"for you)."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् भिन्ननाम्ना विद्यमानसञ्चिकायाः प्रतिलिपिं कर्तुम् इच्छति -- सम्भवतः बैकअपरूपेण -- "
"मूलसञ्चिकायाः समानपुटे, तर्हि सामान्यं <guimenuitem>प्रतिलिपिं</guimenuitem> ततः यदा "
"भवान् <guimenuitem>चिपयति </guimenuitem> it सञ्चिका पूर्वमेव अस्ति इति शिकायतुं "
"संवादपेटिका पोप् अप भविष्यति । केवलं संवादस्य पाठपेटिकायां नूतनं नाम टङ्कयित्वा "
"<guibutton>Continue</guibutton> बटनं नुदन्तु (अथवा यदि भवान् आलस्यं अनुभवति तर्हि "
"<guibutton>Suggest New Name</guibutton> बटनं नुदन् भवतः कृते नूतनं नाम उत्पद्यते) ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring File Associations"
msgstr "सञ्चिकासङ्घस्य विन्यासः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1137
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kde; provides many applications which can open many different types of "
#| "file. Most of the time, the defaults will work with no problems, but "
#| "&konqueror; provides a powerful system to allow you to change the "
#| "applications used to open each file type. For more details, choose the "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror..."
#| "</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, select <guilabel>File "
#| "Associations</guilabel> in the configuration dialog, and click on "
#| "<guibutton>Help</guibutton>."
msgid ""
"&kde; provides many applications which can open many different types of "
"file. Most of the time, the defaults will work with no problems, but "
"&konqueror; provides a powerful system to allow you to change the "
"applications used to open each file type. For more details, choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, select <guilabel>File Associations</"
"guilabel> in the configuration dialog, and click on <guibutton>Help</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"&kde; अनेकाः अनुप्रयोगाः प्रदाति ये अनेकविधाः सञ्चिकाः उद्घाटयितुं शक्नुवन्ति । अधिकांशतः, "
"पूर्वनिर्धारिताः समस्यां विना कार्यं करिष्यन्ति, परन्तु &konqueror; प्रत्येकं सञ्चिकाप्रकारस्य "
"उद्घाटनार्थं प्रयुक्तानि अनुप्रयोगाः परिवर्तयितुं शक्नुवन्ति इति शक्तिशालिनीं प्रणालीं प्रदाति "
"। अधिकविवरणार्थं <menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"Konqueror...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> मेनू-वस्तु चिनोतु, विन्यास-संवादे "
"<guilabel>सञ्चिका-सङ्घटनाः</guilabel> इति चिनोतु , <guibutton>सहायता</"
"guibutton> इत्यत्र नुदन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1150
#, no-c-format
msgid "At the Command Line"
msgstr "आदेशपङ्क्तौ"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although &konqueror; is a very powerful and flexible <acronym>GUI</acronym> "
"file manager, there are occasions when the experienced &Linux; / &UNIX; user "
"wants to get down to the basics and work at the text command line level."
msgstr ""
"यद्यपि &konqueror; अतीव शक्तिशाली लचीला च <acronym>GUI</acronym> सञ्चिकाप्रबन्धकः "
"अस्ति, एतादृशाः अवसराः सन्ति यदा अनुभवी &Linux; / & UNIX; उपयोक्ता मूलभूतविषयेषु अधः "
"गत्वा पाठनिर्देशपङ्क्तिस्तरस्य कार्यं कर्तुम् इच्छति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1157
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can, of course, open an instance of &konsole;, perhaps with "
#| "&konqueror;'s Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Open Terminal</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option or "
#| "with <keycap>F4</keycap>."
msgid ""
"You can, of course, open an instance of &konsole;, perhaps with "
"&konqueror;’s Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open "
"Terminal</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option or with <keycap>F4</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"भवान्, अवश्यं, &konsole;-इत्यस्य एकं उदाहरणं उद्घाटयितुं शक्नोति, सम्भवतः &konqueror;-"
"इत्यस्य Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open "
"Terminal</guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पेन अथवा <keycap> इत्यनेन सह F4</"
"keycap> इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1160
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you only want to launch a program or view a &URL;, the <menuchoice> "
#| "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Execute Shell Command...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</"
#| "keycap></keycombo>) option may be easier."
msgid ""
"If you only want to launch a program or view a &URL;, the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Execute Shell Command…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) "
"option may be easier."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् केवलं कार्यक्रमं प्रारम्भं कर्तुम् इच्छति अथवा &URL; द्रष्टुम् इच्छति तर्हि "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>उपकरणाः</guimenu><guimenuitem>शेल् आदेशं निष्पादयतु...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</"
"keycap></keycombo>) विकल्पः सुलभः भवेत् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1165
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Execute Shell Command... "
#| "</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>E</"
#| "keycap></keycombo>) opens a small command line dialog window where you "
#| "can enter a shell command such as <userinput>ps -ax | grep kdeinit </"
#| "userinput>. Note that it does not support full featured terminal control "
#| "characters, so applications such as <userinput>top</userinput> and "
#| "<userinput> less</userinput> will not work properly, but it is available "
#| "immediately without the delay involved in starting &konsole;."
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Execute Shell Command… </"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>E</"
"keycap></keycombo>) opens a small command line dialog window where you can "
"enter a shell command such as <userinput>ps -ax | grep kdeinit </userinput>. "
"Note that it does not support full featured terminal control characters, so "
"applications such as <userinput>top</userinput> and <userinput> less</"
"userinput> will not work properly, but it is available immediately without "
"the delay involved in starting &konsole;."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>उपकरणाः</guimenu><guimenuitem>शेल् आदेशं निष्पादयन्तु... </"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>E</"
"keycap></keycombo >) एकं लघु आदेशपङ्क्तिसंवादविण्डो उद्घाटयति यत्र भवान् <userinput>ps "
"-ax | इत्यादिकं शेल् आदेशं प्रविष्टुं शक्नोति ग्रेप् क्देइनित् </userinput>. ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु यत् "
"एतत् पूर्णविशेषतायुक्तान् टर्मिनल् नियन्त्रणवर्णान् समर्थयति न, अतः <userinput>top</"
"userinput> तथा <userinput> less</userinput> इत्यादयः अनुप्रयोगाः सम्यक् कार्यं न "
"करिष्यन्ति, परन्तु &konsole इत्यस्य आरम्भे विलम्बं विना तत्क्षणमेव उपलब्धम् अस्ति ;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more complex operations, &konqueror; has another nice feature: the "
"Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Terminal "
"Emulator</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option, which opens up a terminal window "
"as a new view within &konqueror;."
msgstr ""
"अधिकजटिलसञ्चालनार्थं &konqueror; अन्यत् सुन्दरं विशेषता अस्ति: Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>Terminal Emulator दर्शयतु</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पः, यः &konqueror;-अन्तर्गतं नूतनदृश्यरूपेण टर्मिनल्-"
"विण्डो उद्घाटयति"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Including the terminal emulator"
msgstr "टर्मिनल एमुलेटर सहित"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1202
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konqueror; the Web Browser"
msgstr "&konqueror; the Web Browser इति जालपुटम्"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browsing www.konqueror.org"
msgstr "www.konqueror.org ब्राउज् करणम्"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Surfing and Searching"
msgstr "सर्फिंग् तथा अन्वेषणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have a connection to the Internet, you can surf with &konqueror; "
"just as you can with any other browser."
msgstr ""
"एकदा भवतः अन्तर्जालसम्पर्कः जातः चेत्, भवन्तः &konqueror; यथा अन्येन ब्राउजरेण सह भवन्तः "
"शक्नुवन्ति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1217
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Type a &URL; into the Location Toolbar window, press <keysym>Enter</"
#| "keysym> or <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on the "
#| "<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"go-jump.png"
#| "\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
#| "<guibutton>Go</guibutton> button at the right hand end of the Location "
#| "Toolbar, and &konqueror; will download and display that page. If you have "
#| "visited the page before, &konqueror;'s <link linkend=\"path-complete"
#| "\">Automatic Text Completion</link> feature can help you type the &URL; a "
#| "second time. If you want to use one of the web's search engines, "
#| "&konqueror;'s <link linkend=\"enhanced-browsing\"> Web Shortcuts</link> "
#| "feature can make this easier."
msgid ""
"Type a &URL; into the Location Toolbar window, press <keysym>Enter</keysym> "
"or <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"go-jump.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> <guibutton>Go</"
"guibutton> button at the right hand end of the Location Toolbar, and "
"&konqueror; will download and display that page. If you have visited the "
"page before, &konqueror;’s <link linkend=\"path-complete\">Automatic Text "
"Completion</link> feature can help you type the &URL; a second time. If you "
"want to use one of the web’s search engines, &konqueror;’s Web Search "
"Keywords feature can make this easier."
msgstr ""
"एकं &amp;URL इति टङ्कयन्तु; Location Toolbar विण्डो मध्ये, नुदन्तु<keysym> प्रवेश</"
"keysym> वा<mousebutton> वामः</mousebutton> इत्यत्र क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-jump.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon><guibutton> गच्छ</"
"guibutton> स्थानसाधनपट्टिकायाः दक्षिणहस्तस्य अन्ते बटनं, &amp;konqueror; तत् पृष्ठं "
"डाउनलोड् कृत्वा प्रदर्शयिष्यति। यदि भवान् पूर्वं पृष्ठं गतवान्, &amp;konqueror;&#39;s<link "
"linkend=\"path-complete\"> स्वचालित पाठ समाप्ति</link> विशेषता भवन्तं &amp;URL; "
"द्वितीयवारं । यदि भवान् जालस्य अन्वेषणयन्त्रेषु एकं उपयोक्तुं इच्छति तर्हि &amp;konqueror;"
"&#39;s<link linkend=\"enhanced-browsing\"> जाल शॉर्टकट</link> विशेषता एतत् सुलभं "
"कर्तुं शक्नोति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a link in a page to open that link."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> पृष्ठे कस्मिंश्चित् लिङ्के क्लिक् कृत्वा तत् लिङ्क् उद्घाटयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open a link in a new instance of &konqueror;, leaving the old page still "
"visible, &RMB; click on the link and select the <guimenuitem>Open in New "
"Window</guimenuitem> option. Alternatively, you might want to "
"<guimenuitem>Open in New Tab</guimenuitem>. <link linkend=\"tabbrowse"
"\">Tabbed Browsing</link> will let you hold a number of pages in one "
"&konqueror; window and quickly switch between them with a single mouse click."
msgstr ""
"&amp;konqueror;इत्यस्य नूतनदृष्टान्तस्य लिङ्कं उद्घाटयितुं, पुरातनं पृष्ठं अद्यापि दृश्यमानं "
"त्यक्त्वा, &amp;RMB; लिङ्क् इत्यत्र क्लिक् कृत्वा...<guimenuitem> New Window इत्यत्र "
"उद्घाटयन्तु</guimenuitem> विकल्प। वैकल्पिकरूपेण भवन्तः इच्छन्ति वा<guimenuitem> New Tab "
"इत्यत्र उद्घाटयन्तु</guimenuitem> .<link linkend=\"tabbrowse\"> ट्याब्ड् ब्राउजिंग्</"
"link> एकस्मिन् &amp;konqueror; window इति कृत्वा एकेन मूषकस्य क्लिक् कृत्वा तेषां मध्ये "
"शीघ्रं स्विच् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You could also select multiple view modes with <menuchoice><guimenu>Window</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Split View Left/Right</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo>) / "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Split View Top/Bottom</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;"
"<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>) option which will let you see different pages "
"at the same time. This can be useful if you are looking through a "
"complicated set of <acronym>HTML</acronym> pages, but make sure the little "
"link box at the bottom right hand corner is empty when you are doing this."
msgstr ""
"भवान् <menuchoice><guimenu>विण्डो</guimenu> <guimenuitem>विभक्तदृश्यं वाम/दक्षिण</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap) "
"इत्यनेन सह बहुदृश्यविधानानि अपि चिन्वितुं शक्नोति स्म >L</keycap></keycombo>) / "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>विण्डो</guimenu> <guimenuitem>विभक्तदृश्यम् उपरि/अधः</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;"
"<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>) विकल्पः यः भवन्तं एकस्मिन् समये भिन्नानि पृष्ठानि द्रष्टुं "
"शक्नोति । यदि भवान् <acronym>HTML</acronym> पृष्ठानां जटिलसमूहं पश्यति तर्हि एतत् "
"उपयोगी भवितुम् अर्हति, परन्तु एतत् कुर्वन् अधः दक्षिणहस्तकोणे स्थितं लघुलिङ्कपेटिका रिक्तं भवति "
"इति सुनिश्चितं कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To go back to the previous page use the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keysym>Left</keysym></keycombo> shortcut, the <guibutton>Back</guibutton> "
"button on the Toolbar, or the menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option."
msgstr ""
"पूर्वपृष्ठं प्रति गन्तुं <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Left</keysym></"
"keycombo> शॉर्टकट्, टूल्बार इत्यत्र <guibutton>Back</guibutton> बटन्, अथवा मेनूबार "
"इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु <menuchoice><guimenu>गच्छ</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पृष्ठतः</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similarly, once you have gone back you can go forward by using <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Right</keysym></keycombo>, the "
"<guibutton>Forward</guibutton> button, or the menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> option."
msgstr ""
"तथैव एकदा भवन्तः पुनः गतवन्तः तदा भवन्तः <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keysym>Right</keysym></keycombo>, <guibutton>Forward</guibutton> बटन्, अथवा "
"मेनूपट्टिकायाः उपयोगेन अग्रे गन्तुं शक्नुवन्ति <menuchoice><guimenu>गच्छ</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>अग्रे</guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are multiple ways of scrolling the viewing area. One is to use the "
"<keysym>Up</keysym> and <keysym>Down</keysym> keys. You may also use the "
"scrollbar, your mousewheel or the <keysym>PgUp</keysym> and <keysym>PgDn</"
"keysym> keys."
msgstr ""
"दृश्यक्षेत्रं स्क्रॉल कर्तुं बहुविधाः उपायाः सन्ति । एकं <keysym>Up</keysym> तथा "
"<keysym>Down</keysym> कीलयोः उपयोगः । भवान् स्क्रॉलबार, स्वस्य मूषकचक्रम् अथवा "
"<keysym>PgUp</keysym> तथा <keysym>PgDn</keysym> कीलयोः अपि उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to stop a download for any reason then use the &Esc; key, the "
"Toolbar <guibutton>Stop</guibutton> button or the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stop</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> item."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् केनचित् कारणेन डाउनलोड् स्थगयितुम् इच्छति तर्हि &Esc; कीलम्, Toolbar "
"<guibutton>Stop</guibutton> बटनं अथवा Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>दृश्य</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stop</guimenuitem></menuchoice> मदं ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are viewing a web page with the <guilabel>HTML Toolbar</guilabel> "
"enabled you should see two new icons in the toolbar "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"format-font-"
"size-less.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> and <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"format-font-size-more.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon>. Use these to adjust the size of the text in "
"the page if you find it difficult to read. How well this works will depend "
"on how the web page has been constructed."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवान् <guilabel>HTML Toolbar</guilabel> सक्षमं कृत्वा जालपुटं पश्यति तदा भवान् "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"format-font-"
"size-less इति साधनपट्टिकायां नूतनचिह्नद्वयं द्रष्टव्यम् । png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> तथा "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"स्वरूप-फॉन्ट-"
"आकार-अधिक.png\" प्रारूप=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon>. यदि भवन्तः पठितुं कष्टं अनुभवन्ति तर्हि पृष्ठे पाठस्य आकारं समायोजयितुं एतेषां "
"उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु । एतत् कियत् सुष्ठु कार्यं करोति इति जालपुटस्य निर्माणं कथं कृतम् इति अवलम्बते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabbed Browsing"
msgstr "ट्याब्ड् ब्राउजिंग्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By using this feature you can make &konqueror; load multiple web pages in "
"the same window, and switch between them using tabbed pages. This way, you "
"can preload a page <quote>in the background</quote> while you carry on "
"reading another."
msgstr ""
"एतस्य विशेषतायाः उपयोगेन भवान् &konqueror; एकस्मिन् विण्डो मध्ये बहुविधजालपृष्ठानि लोड् "
"कुर्वन्तु, ट्याब्ड् पृष्ठानि उपयुज्य तयोः मध्ये स्विच् कुर्वन्तु । एवं भवन्तः अन्यस्य पठनं कुर्वन्तः "
"पृष्ठे <quote>पृष्ठभूमितः</quote> पूर्वं लोड् कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use tabbed browsing, <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on a link and "
"choose <guimenuitem>Open in New Tab</guimenuitem> from the drop down menu or "
"&MMB; click. The page will be downloaded and displayed as normal, but with "
"tabs across the top of the view, one tab for each page. &LMB; click on a tab "
"to view that page, or you can use the shortcuts <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo> and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> to cycle through the tab pages. Alternatively, "
"you can scroll through the tabs using the mouse <mousebutton>wheel</"
"mousebutton> while the mouse pointer is over the tab bar (presuming that "
"your mouse has one). Also, double-clicking over the empty tab bar space will "
"open a new tab."
msgstr ""
"ट्याब्ड् ब्राउजिंग् इत्यस्य उपयोगाय <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> कस्मिंश्चित् लिङ्क् "
"क्लिक् कृत्वा ड्रॉप् डाउन मेन्यू तः <guimenuitem>Open in New Tab</guimenuitem> इति "
"चिनोतु अथवा &MMB; क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु । पृष्ठं डाउनलोड् कृत्वा सामान्यरूपेण प्रदर्शितं भविष्यति, "
"परन्तु दृश्यस्य उपरि ट्याब्-सहितं, प्रत्येकस्य पृष्ठस्य कृते एकं ट्याब् । &LMB; तत् पृष्ठं द्रष्टुं ट्याब् "
"इत्यत्र क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु, अथवा भवान् <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>,</"
"keycap></keycombo> तथा <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap इति शॉर्टकट् "
"उपयोक्तुं शक्नोति >.</keycap></keycombo> ट्याब् पृष्ठेषु चक्रं कर्तुं । वैकल्पिकरूपेण, मूषकस्य "
"<mousebutton>चक्रस्य</mousebutton> इत्यस्य उपयोगेन ट्याब्स् मध्ये स्क्रॉल कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति "
"यदा मूषकस्य सूचकः ट्याब् पट्टिकायाः उपरि भवति (भवतः मूषकस्य अस्ति इति कल्पयित्वा) । अपि "
"च, रिक्तं ट्याब् बार स्पेस इत्यस्य उपरि द्विवारं क्लिक् करणेन नूतनं ट्याब् उद्घाट्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the <guilabel>Open new tabs in the background</guilabel> option in the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> page of the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> dialog, "
"clicking on a link downloads the page and shows a new tab for it, but the "
"new page will not be displayed until you <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
"click on the tab."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>पृष्ठभूमियां नूतनानि ट्याब्स् उद्घाटयन्तु</guilabel> विकल्पस्य उपयोगेन "
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> संवादस्य <guilabel>सामान्य</guilabel> पृष्ठे, कस्मिंश्चित् "
"लिङ्के क्लिक् करणेन पृष्ठं डाउनलोड् भवति, नूतनं च दर्शयति तस्य कृते ट्याब्, परन्तु यावत् भवन्तः "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> ट्याब् इत्यत्र क्लिक् न कुर्वन्ति तावत् नूतनं पृष्ठं न "
"प्रदर्शितं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1303
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you check the <guilabel>Open links in new tab instead of in new "
#| "window</guilabel> box in the <guimenuitem>General</guimenuitem> page of "
#| "the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
#| "Konqueror... </guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog, &MMB; clicking on a link "
#| "will open it in a new tab page and if you hold the &Shift; key down while "
#| "clicking the &MMB; the link will be opened in a background tab page."
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Open links in new tab instead of in new window</"
"guilabel> box in the <guimenuitem>General</guimenuitem> page of the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror… </"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog, &MMB; clicking on a link will open it in a "
"new tab page and if you hold the &Shift; key down while clicking the &MMB; "
"the link will be opened in a background tab page."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् <menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>विन्यासस्य "
"<guimenuitem>सामान्य</guimenuitem> पृष्ठे <guilabel>नवीनविण्डोमध्ये न तु नूतनट्याब् मध्ये "
"लिङ्कानि उद्घाटय</guilabel> इति पेटीम् अवलोकयति Konqueror... </guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> संवादः, &MMB; लिङ्क् क्लिक् कृत्वा नूतने ट्याब् पृष्ठे उद्घाट्यते तथा च यदि भवान् "
"&Shift; &MMB; लिङ्क् पृष्ठभूमिट्याब् पृष्ठे उद्घाट्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on a tab will bring up a menu with "
"the following options:"
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>राइट्</mousebutton> ट्याब् इत्यत्र क्लिक् करणेन निम्नलिखितविकल्पैः सह मेन्यू "
"दृश्यते ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>New Tab</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>नवीन ट्याब्</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens a new, blank, tabbed page view. You can then download a web page "
"into it by typing the &URL; into the Location Bar or by making a selection "
"from the Bookmark Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"एतेन नूतनं, रिक्तं, ट्याब्ड् पृष्ठदृश्यं उद्घाट्यते । ततः भवान् &URL; Location Bar मध्ये अथवा "
"Bookmark Toolbar तः चयनं कृत्वा ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Duplicate Tab</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>द्वितीयकं ट्याब्</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1324
#, no-c-format
msgid "To create a duplicate tabbed page."
msgstr "डुप्लिकेट् ट्याब्ड् पृष्ठं निर्मातुं ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1328
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Reload Tab</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F5</keycap>)"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>पुनः लोड् ट्याब्</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F5</keycap>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reloads the content of the current tab."
msgstr "वर्तमान ट्याब् इत्यस्य सामग्रीं पुनः लोड् करोति ।"

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: index.docbook:1333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Tabs"
msgstr "अन्ये टब्स्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a submenu showing all other tabs. Choosing a tab from this list "
"makes it the active tab."
msgstr ""
"अन्ये सर्वाणि ट्याब्स् दर्शयन् उपमेनू प्रदर्शयति । अस्मात् सूचीतः ट्याब् चित्वा तत् सक्रिय ट्याब् "
"भवति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Other Tabs</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Reload All Tabs</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F5</"
"keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>अन्य ट्याब्स्</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>सर्व ट्याब्स् पुनः "
"लोड्</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;"
"<keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reloads the content of every tab."
msgstr "प्रत्येकस्य ट्याब् इत्यस्य सामग्रीं पुनः लोड् करोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guisubmenu>Other Tabs</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Close Other Tabs</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guisubmenu>अन्य ट्याब्स्</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>अन्य ट्याब्स्</guimenuitem> बन्दं "
"कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1346
#, no-c-format
msgid "To close all but the selected tab page."
msgstr "चयनितं ट्याब् पृष्ठं विहाय सर्वाणि बन्दं कर्तुं ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Detach Tab</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>ट्याब् विच्छेदं</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option removes the selected tabbed page from the current &konqueror; "
"window and opens it in a new instance of &konqueror;."
msgstr ""
"एषः विकल्पः वर्तमानतः &konqueror; window इति कृत्वा &konqueror; इत्यस्य नूतने उदाहरणे "
"उद्घाटयति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Close Tab</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>ट्याब् बन्दं कुर्वन्तु</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid "To close the selected tab page."
msgstr "चयनितं ट्याब् पृष्ठं बन्दं कर्तुं ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Web Search Keywords"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1367
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If enabled, &konqueror;'s Web Shortcuts feature lets you submit a query "
#| "directly to a search engine or similar web site without having to visit "
#| "the site first."
msgid ""
"If enabled, &konqueror;’s Web Search Keywords feature lets you submit a "
"query directly to a search engine or similar web site without having to "
"visit the site first."
msgstr ""
"यदि सक्षमं भवति तर्हि &konqueror;'s Web Shortcuts विशेषता प्रथमं साइट् गन्तुं विना "
"प्रत्यक्षतया अन्वेषणयन्त्रे अथवा तत्सदृशे जालस्थले प्रश्नं प्रस्तूय कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, entering <userinput>gg:konqueror</userinput> into the Location "
"Bar and pressing <keysym>Enter</keysym> will ask <trademark>Google</"
"trademark> to search for items related to &konqueror;."
msgstr ""
"यथा, <userinput>gg:konqueror</userinput> इति स्थानपट्टिकायां प्रविष्ट्वा "
"<keysym>Enter</keysym> नुदन् <trademark>Google</trademark> इत्यस्मै &konqueror;"
"सम्बद्धानि वस्तूनि अन्वेष्टुं पृच्छति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1368
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the &systemsettings; category <guilabel>Network</guilabel> on the "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Connection "
#| "Preferences</guimenuitem></menuchoice> page."
msgid ""
"To see what Web Search Keywords are available, and perhaps add your own, "
"open the <guilabel>Web Search Keywords</guilabel> page in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> page."
msgstr ""
"&systemsettings इत्यत्र &systemsettings; category <guilabel>जाल</guilabel> "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>संयोजनप्राथमिकता</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> पृष्ठे ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Access Keys"
msgstr "अभिगम कुञ्जी"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; has full support for the <sgmltag class=\"attribute\">accesskey</"
"sgmltag> &HTML; attribute in forms and links. Access keys allow you to use "
"the keyboard keys for functions which would perhaps normally be done with "
"the mouse, such as following links. The benefit of this is, quite simply, "
"that users can interact with a page with devices other than a pointing "
"device."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; <sgmltag class=\"attribute\">प्रवेशकुंजी</sgmltag> &HTML; रूपेषु लिङ्केषु "
"च विशेषता। अभिगमकुंजीः भवन्तं कार्याणां कृते कीबोर्डकीलानां उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति ये सम्भवतः "
"सामान्यतया मूषकेन सह क्रियन्ते, यथा निम्नलिखितलिङ्कानि । अस्य लाभः अस्ति यत्, सरलतया, "
"उपयोक्तारः पृष्ठेन सह सूचकयन्त्रात् परैः उपकरणैः सह अन्तरक्रियां कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature has to be enabled by checking the <guilabel>Enable Access Key "
"activation with &Ctrl; key</guilabel> option on the <guilabel>Web Browsing</"
"guilabel> settings page."
msgstr ""
"एतत् विशेषतां <guilabel>Enable Access Key सक्रियीकरणं &Ctrl; <guilabel>जालभ्रमण</"
"guilabel> सेटिङ्ग्स् पृष्ठे कील</guilabel> विकल्पः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To activate the access keys in &konqueror;, press and release &Ctrl;. Once "
"this is pressed, if a particular link on the website has the <sgmltag class="
"\"attribute\">accesskey</sgmltag> attribute in the given link, then the "
"character(s) should appear over the link, identifying what needs to be "
"pressed. Then, you can enter the character(s) associated with the link as an "
"alternative to following the link with the mouse. To disable the access keys "
"once activated you can press &Ctrl; again."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror;मध्ये अभिगमकुंजीसक्रियीकरणाय &Ctrl; एकदा एतत् निपीडितं जातं चेत्, यदि जालपुटे "
"कस्यचित् विशेषस्य लिङ्कस्य दत्तलिङ्के <sgmltag class=\"attribute\">accesskey</"
"sgmltag> विशेषता अस्ति, तर्हि लिङ्कस्य उपरि वर्णः (वर्णाः) दृश्यन्ते, यत् किं भवितुम् "
"आवश्यकम् इति चिनोति निपीडितम् । ततः, मूषकेन लिङ्कस्य अनुसरणस्य विकल्परूपेण लिङ्केन सह "
"सम्बद्धं वर्णं (वर्णान्) प्रविष्टुं शक्नुवन्ति । एकवारं सक्रियताम् अवाप्त्वा अभिगमकुंजीः निष्क्रियं "
"कर्तुं भवान् &Ctrl; पुनः।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The proper use of this feature requires that the web designer of the page "
"has specifically assigned, using the <sgmltag class=\"attribute\">accesskey</"
"sgmltag> attribute, an access key for the link. Many web designers might not "
"include the <sgmltag class=\"attribute\">accesskey</sgmltag> in their links "
"and forms, and consequently this feature will be unusable on the given "
"webpage."
msgstr ""
"अस्य विशेषतायाः सम्यक् उपयोगाय पृष्ठस्य जालनिर्मातृणा विशेषतया, <sgmltag class="
"\"attribute\">accesskey</sgmltag> विशेषतायाः उपयोगेन, लिङ्कस्य कृते अभिगमकुंजी "
"नियुक्ता इति आवश्यकम् बहवः जालनिर्मातारः स्वस्य लिङ्क्-रूपेषु <sgmltag class=\"attribute"
"\">accesskey</sgmltag> इत्येतत् न समाविष्टं कुर्वन्ति, फलतः दत्तजालपुटे एतत् विशेषता "
"अनुपयोगी भविष्यति"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1405
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browser Identification"
msgstr "ब्राउज़र पहिचान"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &konqueror; connects to a web site it sends some brief browser "
"identification information, known as the <quote>User Agent</quote> string. "
"Many web sites use this information to customize the pages that they send "
"back, based on the strengths and weaknesses of different browsers."
msgstr ""
"यदा &konqueror; जालस्थलेन सह सम्बद्धं भवति तत् काश्चन संक्षिप्तं ब्राउजर्-परिचयसूचनाः "
"प्रेषयति, यत् <quote>उपयोक्तृ-एजेण्ट्</quote> स्ट्रिंग् इति नाम्ना प्रसिद्धम् । अनेकाः "
"जालपुटाः एतां सूचनां उपयुञ्जते यत् ते पृष्ठानि अनुकूलितुं शक्नुवन्ति, ये ते पुनः प्रेषयन्ति, भिन्न-"
"भिन्न-ब्राउजर्-समूहानां सामर्थ्य-दुर्बलता-आधारितं ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, some badly designed sites refuse to work properly unless you "
"are using a browser that the site recognizes as a <quote>valid</quote> one, "
"even though if given a chance, &konqueror; will work satisfactorily with the "
"vast majority of web pages."
msgstr ""
"दुर्भाग्येन केचन दुर्निर्मितानि साइट्-स्थानानि सम्यक् कार्यं कर्तुं नकारयन्ति यावत् भवान् एकं "
"ब्राउजर् न उपयुङ्क्ते यत् साइट् <quote>मान्य</quote> इति परिचिनोति, यद्यपि अवसरः दत्तः, "
"&konqueror; जालपृष्ठानां विशालबहुमतेन सह सन्तोषजनकरूपेण कार्यं करिष्यति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To overcome this problem you can change the browser identification "
"information that &konqueror; sends for specific sites or domains by "
"selecting the <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/useragent/\">Browser "
"Identification</ulink> module in the &systemsettings; category "
"<guilabel>Network</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"एतां समस्यां दूरीकर्तुं भवान् ब्राउजर्-परिचय-सूचनाम् परिवर्तयितुं शक्नोति यत् &konqueror; "
"&systemsettings; category <guilabel>जालम्</guilabel> ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Problems with getting a web page to work properly may also be due to its use "
"of &Java; or JavaScript. If you suspect that this may be the case check that "
"they have been enabled in the <guilabel>Java &amp; JavaScript</guilabel> "
"section of the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"जालपुटस्य सम्यक् कार्यं कर्तुं समस्याः अपि तस्य &Java; अथवा जावास्क्रिप्ट्। यदि भवान् शङ्कते "
"यत् एतत् भवितुं शक्नोति तर्हि ते <guilabel>Java &amp; सेटिङ्ग्स् संवादस्य जावास्क्रिप्ट्</"
"guilabel> विभागः ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1433
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving and Printing Web Items"
msgstr "जालवस्तूनाम् रक्षणं मुद्रणं च"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1435
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you are viewing a web page you can save it (or at least the basic "
#| "&HTML; or similar source text) to your local disk with "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem></"
#| "menuchoice>. If the page you are viewing uses frames, then you will also "
#| "be given the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Frame "
#| "As...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option. <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> "
#| "click in the frame you want to save first."
msgid ""
"When you are viewing a web page you can save it (or at least the basic "
"&HTML; or similar source text) to your local disk with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. If the page you are viewing uses frames, then you will also be "
"given the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Frame As…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option. <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click in "
"the frame you want to save first."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवान् जालपुटं पश्यति तदा भवान् तत् (अथवा न्यूनतया मूलभूतं &HTML; अथवा तत्सदृशं "
"स्रोतपाठं) <menuchoice><guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As...</ "
"इत्यनेन स्वस्य स्थानीयडिस्कमध्ये रक्षितुं शक्नोति। guimenuitem></menuchoice> इति । यदि "
"भवान् यत् पृष्ठं पश्यति तत् फ्रेम्स इत्यस्य उपयोगं करोति तर्हि भवतां कृते "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Frame As...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पः अपि दत्तः भविष्यति । <mousebutton>वाम</"
"mousebutton> प्रथमं यत् फ्रेमं रक्षितुम् इच्छति तस्मिन् नुदन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1444
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the page uses a background image, you can get and save that with the "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Background Image "
#| "As...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option."
msgid ""
"If the page uses a background image, you can get and save that with the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Background Image As…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option."
msgstr ""
"यदि पृष्ठं पृष्ठभूमिप्रतिबिम्बस्य उपयोगं करोति तर्हि <menuchoice><guimenu>सञ्चिका</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>पृष्ठभूमिचित्रं यथा रक्षतु...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"विकल्पेन तत् प्राप्तुं रक्षितुं च शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1448
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "But if what you really want is that glorious picture of the latest "
#| "Ferrari, then <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the image will "
#| "give you a drop-down menu with a <guimenuitem>Save Image As...</"
#| "guimenuitem> option. Be sure to respect the owner's copyright, and ask "
#| "for permission before using any pictures saved this way for anything "
#| "other than your own viewing pleasure."
msgid ""
"But if what you really want is that glorious picture of the latest Ferrari, "
"then <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the image will give you a "
"drop-down menu with a <guimenuitem>Save Image As…</guimenuitem> option. Be "
"sure to respect the owner’s copyright, and ask for permission before using "
"any pictures saved this way for anything other than your own viewing "
"pleasure."
msgstr ""
"परन्तु यदि भवान् यत् वस्तुतः इच्छति तत् नवीनतमस्य फेरारी इत्यस्य तत् गौरवपूर्णं चित्रं अस्ति, "
"तर्हि <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> चित्रे क्लिक् कृत्वा <guimenuitem>Save Image "
"As...</guimenuitem इत्यनेन सह एकं ड्रॉप्-डाउन मेन्यू प्राप्स्यति > विकल्पः । स्वामिनः "
"प्रतिलिपिधर्मस्य आदरं अवश्यं कुर्वन्तु, तथा च स्वस्य दर्शनसुखात् परं किमपि कृते एतादृशरीत्या "
"रक्षितानां चित्राणां उपयोगात् पूर्वं अनुमतिं याचयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1455
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on a link (which may be a "
#| "picture) and select <guimenuitem>Save Link As...</guimenuitem> from the "
#| "pop up menu the basic &HTML; or similar source text will be downloaded "
#| "and saved on your local disk."
msgid ""
"If you <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on a link (which may be a "
"picture) and select <guimenuitem>Save Link As…</guimenuitem> from the pop up "
"menu the basic &HTML; or similar source text will be downloaded and saved on "
"your local disk."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> कस्मिंश्चित् लिङ्क् (यत् चित्रं भवितुम् "
"अर्हति) क्लिक् कृत्वा pop up मेन्यू तः <guimenuitem>Save Link As...</guimenuitem> "
"इति चिनोति तर्हि मूलभूतं &HTML; अथवा तत्सदृशः स्रोतपाठः अवतरणं कृत्वा भवतः "
"स्थानीयडिस्कमध्ये रक्षितः भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on a link (which may be a picture) "
"and choosing <guimenuitem>Copy Link Address</guimenuitem> will copy the "
"&URL; of the link to the clipboard so you can then paste it into, say, an e-"
"mail to a friend telling her about this wonderful new site."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>राइट्</mousebutton> कस्मिंश्चित् लिङ्क् (यत् चित्रं भवितुम् अर्हति) क्लिक् "
"कृत्वा <guimenuitem>Copy Link Address</guimenuitem> इति चयनं कृत्वा &URL; of the "
"link to the clipboard so you can then paste it into, say, एकं मित्रं प्रति ई-मेलं "
"कृत्वा तस्याः अद्भुतस्य नूतनस्य साइट् विषये कथयति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on a picture and choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Copy Image</guimenuitem> copies the &URL; of the picture to the "
"clipboard."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>राइट्</mousebutton> चित्रे क्लिक् कृत्वा <guimenuitem>प्रतिबिम्बं "
"प्रतिलिख्य</guimenuitem> इति चित्वा &URL; चित्रस्य क्लिपबोर्डं प्रति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1469
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Printing a copy of the page you are viewing is easily done with the "
#| "Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <guimenuitem>Print Frame</guimenuitem> "
#| "option or with the Toolbar <guiicon>Print</guiicon> button."
msgid ""
"Printing a copy of the page you are viewing is easily done with the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or <guimenuitem>Print Frame</guimenuitem> option or with the "
"Toolbar <guiicon>Print</guiicon> button."
msgstr ""
"भवन्तः यत् पृष्ठं पश्यन्ति तस्य प्रतिलिपिं मुद्रयितुं Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> अथवा "
"<guimenuitem>Print Frame</guimenuitem इत्यनेन सहजतया भवति > विकल्पः अथवा "
"Toolbar <guiicon>Print</guiicon> बटन् इत्यनेन सह ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1478
#, no-c-format
msgid "&FTP;"
msgstr "&FTP;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&FTP;, or File Transfer Protocol, is one of the earliest, and still perhaps "
"the best, way of transferring files between computers over the Internet."
msgstr ""
"&FTP;, अथवा File Transfer Protocol, अन्तर्जालमाध्यमेन सङ्गणकानां मध्ये सञ्चिकानां "
"स्थानान्तरणस्य प्रारम्भिकेषु, अद्यापि सम्भवतः सर्वोत्तमेषु च मार्गेषु अन्यतमः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1484
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "With &FTP; you can see files and folders on the distant computer just as "
#| "if they were on your own system, download them onto your computer using "
#| "&konqueror;'s normal <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and "
#| "<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> or Drag n' Drop methods and, if allowed, "
#| "upload files from your machine to the other computer's filesystem. To try "
#| "it, type the &URL;"
msgid ""
"With &FTP; you can see files and folders on the distant computer just as if "
"they were on your own system, download them onto your computer using "
"&konqueror;’s normal <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem> or Drag’n Drop methods and, if allowed, upload files from your "
"machine to the other computer’s filesystem. To try it, type the &URL;"
msgstr ""
"&FTP इत्यनेन सह; दूरस्थसङ्गणके सञ्चिकाः, पुटकानि च स्वप्रणाल्यां इव द्रष्टुं शक्नुवन्ति, "
"&konqueror;इत्यस्य सामान्यस्य <guimenuitem>प्रतिलिपि</guimenuitem> इत्यस्य उपयोगेन "
"स्वसङ्गणके डाउनलोड् कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति तथा च <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> अथवा Drag "
"इत्यस्य उपयोगेन n' विधयः पातयन्तु, यदि अनुमतं भवति तर्हि स्वयन्त्रात् अन्यसङ्गणकस्य "
"सञ्चिकातन्त्रे सञ्चिकाः अपलोड् कुर्वन्तु । तस्य प्रयासाय &URL;"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:1491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>ftp://ftp.l10n.kde.org</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>ftp://ftp.l10n.kde.org</userinput> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"into the Location Toolbar and press <keysym>Enter</keysym>. As long as you "
"are connected to the Internet, you should end up seeing the <filename class="
"\"directory\">ftp</filename> folder of the l10n server."
msgstr ""
"Location Toolbar मध्ये गत्वा <keysym>Enter</keysym> नुदन्तु । यावत् भवन्तः "
"अन्तर्जालसङ्गणकेन सह सम्बद्धाः सन्ति तावत् भवन्तः अन्ते l10n सर्वरस्य <filename class="
"\"directory\">ftp</filename> पुटं द्रष्टुं अर्हन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although, strictly speaking, &FTP; &URL;s should be entered starting with "
"<userinput>ftp://</userinput> and <acronym>WWW </acronym> &URL;s starting "
"with <userinput>http://</userinput> &konqueror; is usually smart enough to "
"figure out what is meant, and insert these characters for you if you leave "
"them out."
msgstr ""
"यद्यपि, कठोररूपेण, &FTP; &URL;s <userinput>ftp://</userinput> इत्यनेन आरभ्य "
"<acronym>WWW </acronym> &URL;s <userinput>http://</userinput> इत्यनेन आरभ्य "
"&konqueror; प्रायः स्मार्टः भवति यत् किं अभिप्रेतम् इति चिन्तयति, यदि भवन्तः तान् बहिः "
"त्यजन्ति तर्हि एतानि वर्णाः भवतः कृते निवेशयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you access an &FTP; site it will usually need some form of username and "
"password from you. To simplify things, most &FTP; sites that offer files for "
"free downloading will accept the word <systemitem class=\"username\"> "
"anonymous</systemitem> as a username and your email address as a password, "
"and to make your life even easier &konqueror; will automatically supply "
"these without troubling you."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवान् &FTP; site तस्य प्रायः भवतः कृते उपयोक्तृनामस्य गुप्तशब्दस्य च किञ्चित् प्रकारस्य "
"आवश्यकता भविष्यति । विषयान् सरलीकर्तुं अधिकांशः &FTP; ये साइट्-स्थानानि निःशुल्क-"
"अवलोकनार्थं सञ्चिकाः प्रदास्यन्ति, ते <systemitem class=\"username\"> अनामिक</"
"systemitem> इति शब्दं उपयोक्तृनामरूपेण, भवतः ईमेल-सङ्केतं गुप्तशब्दरूपेण च स्वीकुर्वन्ति, तथा च "
"भवतः जीवनं अधिकं सुलभं कर्तुं &konqueror स्वयमेव एतानि आपूर्तिं करिष्यति भवन्तं न कष्टं ददाति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you try to access an &FTP; site that does not need a proper username or "
"password but which is too busy to accept any more connections, &konqueror; "
"often interprets the <quote>busy</quote> message as a request for a name and "
"password and will therefore pop up a dialog box asking you to supply them."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् &FTP; साइट् यस्य समुचितस्य उपयोक्तृनामस्य गुप्तशब्दस्य वा आवश्यकता नास्ति परन्तु "
"यस्याः व्यस्तता अधिकानि संयोजनानि स्वीकुर्वितुं न शक्नोति, &konqueror; प्रायः "
"<quote>busy</quote> सन्देशस्य व्याख्यां नाम गुप्तशब्दस्य च अनुरोधरूपेण करोति अतः भवन्तं तान् "
"आपूर्तिं कर्तुं पृच्छन् संवादपेटिकां पोप् अप करिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sites that are more concerned with security will need a proper username and "
"password, in which case &konqueror; will ask you for them or you can include "
"the username in the &URL; you type into the Location Toolbar, as for example"
msgstr ""
"सुरक्षायाः विषये अधिकं चिन्तितानां साइट्-स्थानानां समुचितं उपयोक्तृनाम गुप्तशब्दं च आवश्यकं "
"भविष्यति, अस्मिन् सन्दर्भे &konqueror; तान् पृच्छति अथवा भवान् उपयोक्तृनाम &URL; भवन्तः "
"Location Toolbar इत्यत्र टङ्कयन्ति, यथा उदाहरणार्थम्"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:1521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>ftp://<replaceable>username</replaceable>@ftp.l10n.kde.org</"
"userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>ftp://<प्रतिस्थापनीय>उपयोक्तृनाम</replaceable>@ftp.l10n.kde.org</"
"userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1523
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konqueror; will then prompt you for the password."
msgstr "&konqueror; ततः भवन्तं गुप्तशब्दं प्रार्थयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; can also support automatic logins as specified in a <filename>."
"netrc</filename> file. Details of how to enable this feature are given at "
"<ulink url=\"https://konqueror.org/faq/"
"#DoesKonquerorsupportautomaticftploginsvianetrcfiles\"> https://konqueror."
"org/faq/#DoesKonquerorsupportautomaticftploginsvianetrcfiles</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; <filename>.netrc</filename> सञ्चिकायां निर्दिष्टवत् स्वचालितप्रवेशानां "
"समर्थनमपि कर्तुं शक्नोति । एतत् विशेषतां कथं सक्षमं कर्तव्यमिति विवरणं <ulink url="
"\"https://konqueror.org/faq/"
"#DoesKonquerorsupportautomaticftploginsvianetrcfiles\"> https://konqueror."
"org/faq/#DoesKonquerorsupportautomaticftploginsvianetrcfiles</ulink> इत्यत्र "
"दत्तम् अस्ति"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1533
#, no-c-format
msgid "&URL;s with Port Numbers"
msgstr "&URL;s पोर्टसङ्ख्याभिः सह"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you specify a port number in your &URL;, as in for example "
"<userinput>http://intranet.corp.com:1080</userinput>, you might get the "
"error message <quote>Access to restricted port in POST denied</quote>. This "
"is done for security reasons. If you nevertheless need to access a server on "
"this port, just add a key line <screen><userinput>\n"
"OverridenPorts=CommaSeparatedListOfAllowedPorts\n"
"</userinput></screen> to <filename>kio_httprc</filename> in the folder "
"<filename class=\"directory\">$(qtpaths --paths GenericConfigLocation)</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् स्वस्य &URL;मध्ये पोर्ट्-सङ्ख्यां निर्दिशति, यथा उदाहरणार्थं <userinput>http://"
"intranet.corp.com:1080</userinput>, तर्हि भवान् <quote>POST मध्ये प्रतिबन्धित-पोर्ट्-"
"प्रवेशः अङ्गीकृतः इति त्रुटिसन्देशं प्राप्नुयात् </quote> इति । एतत् सुरक्षाकारणात् क्रियते । "
"यदि तथापि भवद्भिः अस्मिन् पोर्ट् मध्ये सर्वरं अभिगन्तुं आवश्यकं भवति तर्हि केवलं "
"<screen><userinput> इति कीलरेखां योजयन्तु\n"
"OverridenPorts=अनुमतपोर्ट्णां अल्पविरामविच्छेदसूची\n"
"</userinput></screen> इत्यनेन <filename class=\"directory\">$(qtpaths --paths "
"GenericConfigLocation)</filename> इति पुटे <filename>kio_httprc</filename> "
"इत्यस्मै ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example <screen><userinput>OverridenPorts=23,15\n"
"</userinput></screen> (it should not include any embedded spaces)."
msgstr ""
"यथा <screen><userinput>OverridenPorts=23,15\n"
"</userinput></screen> (अस्मिन् किमपि एम्बेडेड् रिक्तस्थानानि न समाविष्टानि भवेयुः) ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1545
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konqueror; will reject the following ports:"
msgstr "&konqueror; निम्नलिखित पोर्ट् अङ्गीकुर्वति:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"1, 7, 9, 11, 13, 15, 17, 19, 20, 21, 22, 23, 25, 37, 42, 43, 53, 77, 79, 87, "
"95, 101, 102, 103, 104, 109, 110, 111, 113, 115, 117, 119, 123, 135, 139, "
"143, 179, 389, 512, 513, 514, 515, 526, 530, 531, 532, 540, 556, 587, 601, "
"989, 990, 992, 993, 995, 1080, 2049, 4045, 6000, 6667"
msgstr ""
"१, ७, ९, ११, १३, १५, १७, १९, २०, २१, २२, २३, २५, ३७, ४२, ४३, ५३, ७७, ७९, ८७, "
"९५, १०१, १०२, १०३, १०४, ९. १०९, ११०, १११, ९. ११३, ११५, ११७, ११९, १२३, १३५, "
"१३९, १४३, १७९, ३८९, ५१२, ५१३, ५१४, ५१५, ५२६, ५३०, ५३१, ५३२, ५४०, ५५६, ५८७, "
"६०१, ९८९, ९. ९९०, ९९२, ९९३, ९९५, १०८०, २०४९, ४०४५, ६०००, ६६६७"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Text Completion"
msgstr "स्वचालित पाठ समाप्ति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can get &konqueror; to help you enter a path or &URL; into the Location "
"Toolbar by enabling one of the <guimenuitem>Text Completion</guimenuitem> "
"features. To do this <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on a clear part "
"of the Location Toolbar text entry box and select <guisubmenu>Text "
"Completion</guisubmenu> from the pop up menu. This will let you choose "
"between the following options:"
msgstr ""
"भवन्तः &konqueror; भवतः मार्गं प्रविष्टुं सहायतार्थं अथवा &URL; "
"<guimenuitem>पाठसमाप्तिः</guimenuitem> इति विशेषतासु एकं सक्षमं कृत्वा Location "
"Toolbar मध्ये प्रवेशं कुर्वन्तु । एतत् कर्तुं <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> Location "
"Toolbar पाठप्रविष्टिपेटिकायाः स्पष्टभागे क्लिक् कृत्वा pop up मेन्यूतः <guisubmenu>Text "
"Completion</guisubmenu> इति चिनोतु । एतेन भवन्तः निम्नलिखितविकल्पानां मध्ये चयनं कर्तुं "
"शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1582
#, no-c-format
msgid "None"
msgstr "न कश्चित्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1583
#, no-c-format
msgid "What you get is what you type."
msgstr "यत् भवन्तः प्राप्नुवन्ति तत् भवन्तः टङ्कयन्ति।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manual"
msgstr "शास्त्र"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1589
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have typed part of a path or &URL;, pressing <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> or &Tab; will complete the "
"entry if it is possible to do so unambiguously."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवान् मार्गस्य भागं अथवा &URL;, टङ्कितवान् तदा <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> अथवा &Tab; यदि निर्विवादरूपेण कर्तुं शक्यते "
"तर्हि प्रविष्टिं सम्पूर्णं करिष्यति।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1595
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic"
msgstr "स्वतः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1596
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As you type into the Location Toolbar window &konqueror; will "
#| "automatically extend what you type to complete one possible path or "
#| "&URL;, highlighting the characters it has added. Continue typing if "
#| "that's not what you wanted or press <keysym>Enter</keysym> to accept it."
msgid ""
"As you type into the Location Toolbar window &konqueror; will automatically "
"extend what you type to complete one possible path or &URL;, highlighting "
"the characters it has added. Continue typing if that’s not what you wanted "
"or press <keysym>Enter</keysym> to accept it."
msgstr ""
"यथा भवान् Location Toolbar विण्डो मध्ये टङ्कयति &konqueror; एकं सम्भाव्यं मार्गं अथवा "
"&URL;, पूर्णं कर्तुं यत् टङ्कयति तत् स्वयमेव विस्तारयिष्यति, तया योजितवर्णान् प्रकाशयिष्यति । "
"यदि भवान् तत् न इच्छति तर्हि टङ्कनं निरन्तरं कुर्वन्तु अथवा तत् स्वीकुर्वन्तु <keysym>Enter</"
"keysym> नुदन्तु ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1600
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dropdown List"
msgstr "ड्रॉपडाउन सूची"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A drop-down window will appear as you type, showing the possible matches to "
"what you have typed so far. When the path or &URL; that you want appears in "
"the window click on it with the &LMB;. You can also use the <keysym>Down</"
"keysym> or &Tab; and <keysym>Up</keysym> or <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Shift;&Tab;</keycombo> keys to select it then press <keysym>Enter</"
"keysym>."
msgstr ""
"यथा भवन्तः टङ्कयन्ति तथा एकं पतत्-विण्डो दृश्यते, यत् भवता एतावता टङ्कितस्य सम्भाव्यमेलनानि "
"दर्शयति । यदा मार्गः अथवा &URL; यत् भवान् इच्छति तत् &LMB; इत्यनेन सह तस्मिन् क्लिक् "
"कृत्वा विण्डो मध्ये दृश्यते । <keysym>Down</keysym> अथवा &Tab; तथा च <keysym>Up</"
"keysym> अथवा <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Tab;</keycombo> कीलानि "
"चिन्वन्तु ततः <keysym>Enter</keysym> नुदन्तु ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1611
#, no-c-format
msgid "Short Automatic"
msgstr "लघु स्वचालित"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is like Automatic mode except that it only extends what you have typed "
"as far as the next <keycap>/</keycap> symbol in the path or &URL;. Press "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> or &Tab; to "
"accept the suggestion, <keysym>Enter</keysym> when the complete path or "
"&URL; is shown."
msgstr ""
"इदं Automatic mode इव अस्ति केवलं भवता टङ्कितं केवलं मार्गे अथवा &URL;. <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> अथवा &Tab; सुझावं "
"स्वीकुर्वितुं, <keysym>प्रविष्ट</keysym> यदा सम्पूर्णः मार्गः अथवा &URL; इति दर्शितम् ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1620
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dropdown List &amp; Automatic"
msgstr "ड्रॉपडाउन सूची &amp; स्वतः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1621
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is a combination of both options described above."
msgstr "एषः पूर्वोक्तयोः विकल्पयोः संयोजनम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1625
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default"
msgstr "मूलभूतम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item appears at the bottom of the submenu and enables you to switch to "
"the default behaviour <guimenuitem>Dropdown List</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"एतत् द्रव्यं उपमेनूस्य अधः दृश्यते तथा च पूर्वनिर्धारितव्यवहारं <guimenuitem>Dropdown List</"
"guimenuitem> प्रति स्विच् कर्तुं समर्थयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should try out these different modes and pick the one that suits you "
"best."
msgstr "एतानि भिन्नानि गुणाः परीक्ष्य भवतः अनुकूलं गुणं चिन्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1650
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Bookmarks"
msgstr "बुकमार्कस्य उपयोगः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1652
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Although you can use &konqueror;'s bookmarks to record the locations of "
#| "your own files and folders, they are most useful when you are surfing the "
#| "Web, letting you build up a list of useful sites."
msgid ""
"Although you can use &konqueror;’s bookmarks to record the locations of your "
"own files and folders, they are most useful when you are surfing the Web, "
"letting you build up a list of useful sites."
msgstr ""
"यद्यपि भवान् स्वकीयानां सञ्चिकानां, पुटस्य च स्थानानि अभिलेखयितुं &konqueror;इत्यस्य "
"पुस्तकचिह्नानां उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोति तथापि यदा भवान् जालपुटे भ्रमणं करोति तदा ते सर्वाधिकं "
"उपयोगिनो भवन्ति, येन भवान् उपयोगीस्थलानां सूचीं निर्मातुम् अर्हति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> menu <mousebutton>left</"
"mousebutton> click on the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> menu. Once the list "
"is visible, you can navigate through it with the arrow keys or with your "
"mouse, then press <keysym>Enter</keysym> or <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
"click to visit the selected location."
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> मेन्यू <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> उद्घाटयितुं "
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> मेन्यू नुदन्तु । एकदा सूची दृश्यते चेत्, भवान् बाणकुंजीभिः "
"अथवा मूषकेन सह तस्याः माध्यमेन गन्तुं शक्नोति, ततः चयनितस्थानं गन्तुं <keysym>Enter</"
"keysym> अथवा <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> नुदतु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
