#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The folder <filename class=\"directory\">kio_http/</filename> in <filename "
"class=\"directory\">qtpaths --paths GenericCacheLocation</filename> contains "
"the browser cache."
msgstr ""
"<filename class=\"directory\">qtpaths --paths GenericCacheLocation</"
"filename> इत्यस्मिन् <filename class=\"directory\">kio_http/</filename> इति पुटे "
"ब्राउजर्-सञ्चयम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any folder specific view settings are put into <literal role=\"extension\">."
"directory</literal> files in the individual folders."
msgstr ""
"यत्किमपि पुटविशिष्टं दृश्यसेटिंग्स् व्यक्तिगतपुटेषु <literal role=\"extension\">.directory</"
"literal> सञ्चिकासु स्थापितानि भवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3557
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I clear out the history file?"
msgstr "इतिहाससञ्चिकां कथं स्वच्छं करोमि ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3558
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two <quote>histories</quote>:"
msgstr "तत्र द्वौ <quote>इतिहासौ</quote>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One is used for text completion in the Location Toolbar text entry box. To "
"clear this <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on the text entry box and "
"select <guimenuitem>Clear History </guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"एकं Location Toolbar पाठप्रविष्टिपेटिकायां पाठसमाप्त्यर्थं उपयुज्यते । एतत् "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> स्वच्छं कर्तुं पाठप्रविष्टिपेटिकायां क्लिक् कृत्वा "
"<guimenuitem>Clear History </guimenuitem> इति चिनोतु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The other is the log of visited locations. Select <guimenuitem>Show History</"
"guimenuitem> in the menu <guimenu>Go</guimenu> and <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click on an entry and choose <guimenuitem>Remove Entry</"
"guimenuitem> (&Del;) to remove just that entry or <guimenuitem>Clear "
"History</guimenuitem> to delete all entries."
msgstr ""
"अन्यः भ्रमणस्थानानां लॉगः अस्ति । मेनू <guimenu>Go</guimenu> मध्ये "
"<guimenuitem>इतिहासं दर्शयतु</guimenuitem> इति चित्वा <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> कस्यापि प्रविष्टेः उपरि क्लिक् कृत्वा <guimenuitem>प्रविष्टिं निष्कासयतु</"
"guimenuitem> (&Del;) इति चिनोतु केवलं तां प्रविष्टिं निष्कासयन्तु अथवा सर्वाणि प्रविष्टयः "
"विलोपयितुं <guimenuitem>इतिहासं स्वच्छं कुर्वन्तु</guimenuitem> ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the application &sweeper; from the kdeutils module which "
"allows you to clean up cookies, favicons, web history and cache, form "
"completion entries and cache policies of visited websites."
msgstr ""
"भवन्तः &sweeper; kdeutils मॉड्यूलतः यत् भवन्तं कुकीज, favicons, जाल-इतिहासः तथा च "
"cache, प्रपत्र-समाप्ति-प्रविष्टयः, आगतानां वेबसाइट्-स्थानानां cache-नीतयः च स्वच्छं कर्तुं "
"शक्नोति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3578
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I enable, disable or clear the browser cache?"
msgstr "ब्राउजर्-सञ्चयं कथं सक्षमं, अक्षमं वा स्वच्छं वा करोमि?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3580
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you select <menuchoice><guimenu>Web Browsing</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Cache</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the dialog "
#| "launched by selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror... </guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
#| "you will be presented with a dialog box that lets you disable the cache, "
#| "clear it or set its size, and change the caching policy."
msgid ""
"If you select <menuchoice><guimenu>Web Browsing</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cache</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the dialog launched by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, you will be presented with a dialog box that lets "
"you disable the cache, clear it or set its size, and change the caching "
"policy."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् <menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"Konqueror इति चित्वा प्रारब्धसंवादे <menuchoice><guimenuitem>जालब्राउजिंग्</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Cache</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> इति चिनोति .. </"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, भवद्भ्यः एकं संवादपेटिका प्रस्तुतं भविष्यति यत् भवन्तः कैशं "
"निष्क्रियं कर्तुं, तत् स्वच्छं कर्तुं वा सेट् कर्तुं वा शक्नुवन्ति तस्य आकारः, तथा च संग्रहणनीतिं "
"परिवर्तयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3585
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "How do I set my <quote>home</quote> page - the page loaded on startup?"
msgid "How do I set my <quote>home</quote> page—the page loaded on startup?"
msgstr "मम <quote>home</quote> पृष्ठं - आरम्भे लोड् कृतं पृष्ठं - कथं सेट् करोमि ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; has a <guilabel>Home Folder</guilabel> used in file manager mode "
"and a <guilabel>Home Page</guilabel> used in browser mode."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; सञ्चिकाप्रबन्धकविधाने उपयुज्यमानं <guilabel>गृहपुटं</guilabel> अस्ति तथा च "
"ब्राउजर्विधाने उपयुज्यमानं <guilabel>गृहपृष्ठं</guilabel> अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3590
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To change these settings launch <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror</guimenuitem><guilabel>General</"
#| "guilabel></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"To change these settings launch <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror…</guimenuitem><guilabel>General</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"एतानि सेटिङ्ग्स् परिवर्तयितुं <menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konqueror विन्यस्य</guimenuitem><guilabel>सामान्य</"
"guilabel></menuchoice> प्रारभत ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set the &konqueror; startup page in filemanager mode select "
"<guilabel>Show Introduction Page</guilabel>, <guilabel>Show My Home Page</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Show Blank Page</guilabel> or <guilabel>Show My "
"Bookmarks</guilabel> from the drop down box labeled <guilabel>When Konqueror "
"starts</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; सञ्चिकाप्रबन्धकविधाने प्रारम्भपृष्ठं <guilabel>परिचयपृष्ठं दर्शयतु</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>मम मुखपृष्ठं दर्शयतु</guilabel>, <guilabel>रिक्तपृष्ठं दर्शयतु</guilabel> अथवा "
"<guilabel>मम पुस्तकचिह्नं दर्शयतु</guilabel> इति चिनोतु <guilabel>यदा Konqueror "
"आरभ्यते</guilabel> इति लेबलयुक्तात् अधः पेटीतः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In browser mode &konqueror; starts with the <guilabel>Home page</guilabel> "
"entry."
msgstr ""
"ब्राउजर् मोड् मध्ये &konqueror; <guilabel>Home page</guilabel> इति प्रविष्ट्या आरभ्यते "
"।"

#. Tag: para
